<p data-start="1911" data-end="1934">Python will break here.</p>
<p data-start="1936" data-end="1952">Correct version:</p>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="1954" data-end="2704"><div class="relative w-full mt-4 mb-1"><div class=""><div class="relative"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"><div class="border border-token-border-light border-radius-3xl corner-superellipse/1.1 rounded-3xl"><div class="h-full w-full border-radius-3xl bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary corner-superellipse/1.1 overflow-clip rounded-3xl lxnfua_clipPathFallback"><div class="sticky z-2 select-none top-(--sticky-padding-top)"><div class="flex w-full items-center justify-between py-1.5 ps-4 pe-1.5 font-sans md:ps-5 bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary"><div class="flex max-w-[75%] min-w-0 cursor-default items-center text-sm font-medium justify-self-start text-token-text-primary"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-sm me-2.5 shrink-0"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-ni7q5mnh.svg#e45ab3" fill="currentColor"></use></svg>Python</div><div class="flex flex-row items-center gap-0.5 justify-self-end"><button class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none py-2 text-sm font-medium hover:bg-black/5 dark:hover:bg-white/10 size-9 rounded-full px-2" aria-label="Copy" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-md"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-ni7q5mnh.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button><button class="btn relative group-focus-within/dialog:focus-visible:[outline-width:1.5px] group-focus-within/dialog:focus-visible:[outline-offset:2.5px] group-focus-within/dialog:focus-visible:[outline-style:solid] group-focus-within/dialog:focus-visible:[outline-color:var(--text-primary)] btn-ghost border-token-border-default ms-2 border font-sans" aria-label="Run code" type="button"><div class="flex w-full items-center justify-center gap-1.5"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-label="" class="-ms-0.5 icon"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-ni7q5mnh.svg#6ef7a4" fill="currentColor"></use></svg>Run</div></button></div></div></div><div class="pointer-events-none absolute inset-x-4 top-12 bottom-4"><div class="pointer-events-none sticky z-40 shrink-0 z-1!" style="top: calc(calc(var(--sticky-padding-top) + 48px) - 1px * 3); margin-bottom: calc(-4px); height: calc(4px); mask-image: linear-gradient(transparent 25%, white 75%);"><div class="sticky bg-token-border-light" style="top: calc(var(--sticky-padding-top) + 48px); height: 1px;"></div></div></div><div class="" style="transform: none;"><div class="relative z-0 flex max-w-full"><div id="code-block-viewer" dir="ltr" class="q9tKkq_viewer cm-editor z-10 light:cm-light dark:cm-light flex h-full w-full flex-col items-stretch ͼk ͼy"><div class="cm-scroller"><div class="cm-content q9tKkq_readonly"><span class="ͼn">def</span><span> </span><span class="ͼt">_append_log</span><span>(</span><span class="ͼt">self</span><span>, </span><span class="ͼt">msg</span><span>, </span><span class="ͼt">level</span><span class="ͼn">=</span><span class="ͼr">"INFO"</span><span>):</span><br><span>    </span><span class="ͼn">if</span><span> </span><span class="ͼt">self</span><span class="ͼn">.</span><span>server_tab </span><span class="ͼn">is</span><span> </span><span class="ͼn">not</span><span> </span><span class="ͼq">None</span><span>:</span><br><br><span>        </span><span class="ͼt">self</span><span class="ͼn">.</span><span>server_tab</span><span class="ͼn">.</span><span>gpu_status_display</span><span class="ͼn">.</span><span>setPlainText(</span><span class="ͼt">msg</span><span>)</span><br><br><span>        </span><span class="ͼt">target_output</span><span> </span><span class="ͼn">=</span><span> </span><span class="ͼt">getattr</span><span>(</span><span class="ͼt">self</span><span class="ͼn">.</span><span>server_tab, </span><span class="ͼr">"output"</span><span>, </span><span class="ͼq">None</span><span>)</span><br><span>        </span><span class="ͼn">if</span><span> </span><span class="ͼn">not</span><span> </span><span class="ͼt">target_output</span><span>:</span><br><span>            </span><span class="ͼn">return</span><br><br><span>        </span><span class="ͼt">cursor</span><span> </span><span class="ͼn">=</span><span> </span><span class="ͼt">target_output</span><span class="ͼn">.</span><span>textCursor()</span><br><span>        </span><span class="ͼt">cursor</span><span class="ͼn">.</span><span>movePosition(</span><span class="ͼt">QTextCursor</span><span class="ͼn">.</span><span>End)</span><br><br><span>        </span><span class="ͼt">fmt</span><span> </span><span class="ͼn">=</span><span> </span><span class="ͼt">QTextCharFormat</span><span>()</span><br><br><span>        </span><span class="ͼt">colors</span><span> </span><span class="ͼn">=</span><span> {</span><br><span>            </span><span class="ͼr">"INFO"</span><span>: </span><span class="ͼr">"#00ff66"</span><span>,</span><br><span>            </span><span class="ͼr">"WARNING"</span><span>: </span><span class="ͼr">"#ffcc00"</span><span>,</span><br><span>            </span><span class="ͼr">"ERROR"</span><span>: </span><span class="ͼr">"#ff4444"</span><span>,</span><br><span>            </span><span class="ͼr">"CRITICAL"</span><span>: </span><span class="ͼr">"#ff0000"</span><br><span>        }</span><br><br><span>        </span><span class="ͼt">fmt</span><span class="ͼn">.</span><span>setForeground(</span><span class="ͼt">QColor</span><span>(</span><span class="ͼt">colors</span><span class="ͼn">.</span><span>get(</span><span class="ͼt">level</span><span>, </span><span class="ͼr">"#ffffff"</span><span>)))</span><br><br><span>        </span><span class="ͼt">cursor</span><span class="ͼn">.</span><span>insertText(</span><span class="ͼr">f"</span><span>{</span><span class="ͼt">msg</span><span>}</span><span class="ͼx">\n</span><span class="ͼr">"</span><span>, </span><span class="ͼt">fmt</span><span>)</span><br><br><span>        </span><span class="ͼt">target_output</span><span class="ͼn">.</span><span>setTextCursor(</span><span class="ͼt">cursor</span><span>)</span><br><span>        </span><span class="ͼt">target_output</span><span class="ͼn">.</span><span>ensureCursorVisible()</span></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=""><div class="" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"></div></div></div></div></div></pre>
<hr data-start="2706" data-end="2709">
<h1 data-section-id="ymyu8q" data-start="2711" data-end="2745">⚡ Major Improvements I Recommend</h1>
<p data-start="2747" data-end="2833">Since your goal is <strong data-start="2766" data-end="2800">institutional-level trading AI</strong>, here are the <strong data-start="2815" data-end="2832">next upgrades</strong>.</p>
<h2 data-section-id="6dsbho" data-start="2835" data-end="2868">1️⃣ Asynchronous socket server</h2>
<p data-start="2869" data-end="2902">Right now the socket is blocking.</p>
<p data-start="2904" data-end="2911">Better:</p>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="2913" data-end="2939"><div class="relative w-full mt-4 mb-1"><div class=""><div class="relative"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"><div class="border border-token-border-light border-radius-3xl corner-superellipse/1.1 rounded-3xl"><div class="h-full w-full border-radius-3xl bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary corner-superellipse/1.1 overflow-clip rounded-3xl lxnfua_clipPathFallback"><div class="pointer-events-none absolute end-1.5 top-1 z-2 md:end-2 md:top-1"><button class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none pointer-events-auto py-2 text-sm font-medium hover:bg-black/5 dark:hover:bg-white/10 size-9 rounded-full px-2" aria-label="Copy" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-md"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-ni7q5mnh.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button></div><div class="pt-3" style="transform: none;"><div class="relative z-0 flex max-w-full"><div id="code-block-viewer" dir="ltr" class="q9tKkq_viewer cm-editor z-10 light:cm-light dark:cm-light flex h-full w-full flex-col items-stretch ͼk ͼy"><div class="cm-scroller"><div class="cm-content q9tKkq_readonly"><span>asyncio TCP server</span></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=""><div class="" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"></div></div></div></div></div></pre>
<p data-start="2941" data-end="2950">Benefits:</p>
<ul data-start="2952" data-end="3031">
<li data-section-id="mcxs5y" data-start="2952" data-end="2981">
<p data-start="2954" data-end="2981">faster MT4 message handling</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="3c0zvy" data-start="2982" data-end="3009">
<p data-start="2984" data-end="3009">supports multiple clients</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1x8au05" data-start="3010" data-end="3031">
<p data-start="3012" data-end="3031">prevents GUI freeze</p>
</li>
</ul>
<hr data-start="3033" data-end="3036">
<h2 data-section-id="14fry2p" data-start="3038" data-end="3066">2️⃣ Streaming predictions</h2>
<p data-start="3067" data-end="3086">Instead of polling:</p>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="3088" data-end="3137"><div class="relative w-full mt-4 mb-1"><div class=""><div class="relative"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"><div class="border border-token-border-light border-radius-3xl corner-superellipse/1.1 rounded-3xl"><div class="h-full w-full border-radius-3xl bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary corner-superellipse/1.1 overflow-clip rounded-3xl lxnfua_clipPathFallback"><div class="pointer-events-none absolute end-1.5 top-1 z-2 md:end-2 md:top-1"><button class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none pointer-events-auto py-2 text-sm font-medium hover:bg-black/5 dark:hover:bg-white/10 size-9 rounded-full px-2" aria-label="Copy" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-md"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-ni7q5mnh.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button></div><div class="pt-3" style="transform: none;"><div class="relative z-0 flex max-w-full"><div id="code-block-viewer" dir="ltr" class="q9tKkq_viewer cm-editor z-10 light:cm-light dark:cm-light flex h-full w-full flex-col items-stretch ͼk ͼy"><div class="cm-scroller"><div class="cm-content q9tKkq_readonly"><span>MT4 → tick data → AI → prediction → order</span></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=""><div class="" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"></div></div></div></div></div></pre>
<p data-start="3139" data-end="3148">Pipeline:</p>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="3150" data-end="3247"><div class="relative w-full mt-4 mb-1"><div class=""><div class="relative"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"><div class="border border-token-border-light border-radius-3xl corner-superellipse/1.1 rounded-3xl"><div class="h-full w-full border-radius-3xl bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary corner-superellipse/1.1 overflow-clip rounded-3xl lxnfua_clipPathFallback"><div class="pointer-events-none absolute end-1.5 top-1 z-2 md:end-2 md:top-1"><button class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none pointer-events-auto py-2 text-sm font-medium hover:bg-black/5 dark:hover:bg-white/10 size-9 rounded-full px-2" aria-label="Copy" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-md"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-ni7q5mnh.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button></div><div class="pt-3" style="transform: none;"><div class="relative z-0 flex max-w-full"><div id="code-block-viewer" dir="ltr" class="q9tKkq_viewer cm-editor z-10 light:cm-light dark:cm-light flex h-full w-full flex-col items-stretch ͼk ͼy"><div class="cm-scroller"><div class="cm-content q9tKkq_readonly"><span>Tick</span><br><span> ↓</span><br><span>Feature builder</span><br><span> ↓</span><br><span>Model prediction</span><br><span> ↓</span><br><span>Risk filter</span><br><span> ↓</span><br><span>Trade decision</span><br><span> ↓</span><br><span>Execution</span></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=""><div class="" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"></div></div></div></div></div></pre>
<hr data-start="3249" data-end="3252">
<h2 data-section-id="8oc83x" data-start="3254" data-end="3280">3️⃣ Prediction pipeline</h2>
<p data-start="3282" data-end="3337">Right now the system loads model and predicts manually.</p>
<p data-start="3339" data-end="3356">Better structure:</p>
