<h1 data-section-id="19kmoou" data-start="359" data-end="400">✅ Best TensorFlow Setup (2026 – Stable)</h1>
<p data-start="402" data-end="479">For <strong data-start="406" data-end="444">Windows + trading AI + PySide6 GUI</strong>, the most reliable combination is:</p>
<div class="TyagGW_tableContainer"><div tabindex="-1" class="group TyagGW_tableWrapper flex flex-col-reverse w-fit"><table data-start="481" data-end="650" class="w-fit min-w-(--thread-content-width)"><thead data-start="481" data-end="516"><tr data-start="481" data-end="516"><th data-start="481" data-end="493" data-col-size="sm" class="">Component</th><th data-start="493" data-end="516" data-col-size="sm" class="">Recommended Version</th></tr></thead><tbody data-start="527" data-end="650"><tr data-start="527" data-end="548"><td data-start="527" data-end="536" data-col-size="sm">Python</td><td data-start="536" data-end="548" data-col-size="sm"><strong data-start="538" data-end="546">3.10</strong></td></tr><tr data-start="549" data-end="574"><td data-start="549" data-end="562" data-col-size="sm">TensorFlow</td><td data-start="562" data-end="574" data-col-size="sm"><strong data-start="564" data-end="572">2.15</strong></td></tr><tr data-start="575" data-end="595"><td data-start="575" data-end="583" data-col-size="sm">NumPy</td><td data-start="583" data-end="595" data-col-size="sm"><strong data-start="585" data-end="593">1.26</strong></td></tr><tr data-start="596" data-end="630"><td data-start="596" data-end="618" data-col-size="sm">CUDA (optional GPU)</td><td data-start="618" data-end="630" data-col-size="sm"><strong data-start="620" data-end="628">11.8</strong></td></tr><tr data-start="631" data-end="650"><td data-start="631" data-end="639" data-col-size="sm">cuDNN</td><td data-start="639" data-end="650" data-col-size="sm"><strong data-start="641" data-end="648">8.6</strong></td></tr></tbody></table><div class="sticky h-0 select-none end-(--thread-content-margin) self-end"><div class="absolute end-0 flex items-end" style="height: 32.7969px;"><span class="" data-state="closed"><button aria-label="Copy table" class="hover:bg-token-bg-tertiary text-token-text-secondary my-1 rounded-sm p-1 transition-opacity group-[:not(:hover):not(:focus-within)]:pointer-events-none group-