<p data-start="1674" data-end="1699">These two <strong data-start="1684" data-end="1698">must match</strong>.</p>
<hr data-start="1701" data-end="1704">
<h1 data-section-id="hawfdd" data-start="1706" data-end="1736">🚀 How to Install Using This</h1>
<p data-start="1738" data-end="1765">Inside your project folder:</p>
