iv id="code-block-viewer" dir="ltr" class="q9tKkq_viewer cm-editor z-10 light:cm-light dark:cm-light flex h-full w-full flex-col items-stretch ͼk ͼy"><div class="cm-scroller"><div class="cm-content q9tKkq_readonly"><span>pip install </span><span class="ͼu">-e</span><span> .</span></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=""><div class="" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"></div></div></div></div></div></pre>
<hr data-start="1862" data-end="1865">
<h1 data-section-id="1wurrrd" data-start="1867" data-end="1903">📦 Project Structure (Recommended)</h1>
<p data-start="1905" data-end="1945">Your repo should ideally look like this:</p>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="1947" data-end="2129"><div class="relative w-full mt-4 mb-1"><div class=""><div class="relative"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"><div class="border border-token-border-light border-radius-3xl corner-superellipse/1.1 rounded-3xl"><div class="h-full w-full border-radius-3xl bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary corner-superellipse/1.1 overflow-clip rounded-3xl lxnfua_clipPathFallback"><div class="pointer-events-none absolute end-1.5 top-1 z-2 md:end-2 md:top-1"><button class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none pointer-events-auto py-2 text-sm font-medium hover:bg-black/5 dark:hover:bg-white/10 size-9 rounded-full px-2" aria-label="Copy" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-md"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-ni7q5mnh.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button></div><div class="pt-3" style="transform: none;"><div class="relative z-0 flex max-w-full"><div id="code-block-viewer" dir="ltr" class="q9tKkq_viewer cm-editor z-10 light:cm-light dark:cm-light flex h-full w-full flex-col items-stretch ͼk ͼy"><div class="cm-scroller"><div class="cm-content q9tKkq_readonly"><span>Mt4PredictServer</span><br><span>│</span><br><span>├── pyproject.toml</span><br><span>├── README.md</span><br><span>│</span><br><span>├── model/</span><br><span>│   └── model.keras</span><br><span>│</span><br><span>├── src/</span><br><span>│   ├── server/</span><br><span>│   ├── components/</span><br><span>│   ├── frames/</span><br><span>│   └── logs/</span><br><span>│</span><br><span>└── tests/</span></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=""><div class="" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"></div></div></div></div></div></pre>
<p data-start="2131" data-end="2192">This works perfectly with the <code data-start="2161" data-end="2177">pyproject.toml</code> configuration.</p>
<hr data-start="2194" data-end="2197">
<h1 data-section-id="14x6p9d" data-start="2199" data-end="2228">🔥 Pro Tip for Your Project</h1>
<p data-start="2230" data-end="2256">Because your system mixes:</p>
<ul data-start="2258" data-end="2304">
<li data-section-id="da7ij7" data-start="2258" data-end="2267">
<p data-start="2260" data-end="2267"><strong data-start="2260" data-end="2267">GUI</strong></p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1atyoiz" data-start="2268" data-end="2284">
<p data-start="2270" data-end="2284"><strong data-start="2270" data-end="2284">TensorFlow</strong></p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="6lagp4" data-start="2285" data-end="2304">
<p data-start="2287" data-end="2304"><strong data-start="2287" data-end="2304">socket server</strong></p>
</li>
</ul>
<p data-start="2306" data-end="2341">the best architecture long term is:</p>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="2343" data-end="2459"><div class="relative w-full mt-4 mb-1"><div class=""><div class="relative"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"><div class="border border-token-border-light border-radius-3xl corner-superellipse/1.1 rounded-3xl"><div class="h-full w-full border-radius-3xl bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary corner-superellipse/1.1 overflow-clip rounded-3xl lxnfua_clipPathFallback"><div class="pointer-events-none absolute end-1.5 top-1 z-2 md:end-2 md:top-1"><button class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none pointer-events-auto py-2 text-sm font-medium hover:bg-black/5 dark:hover:bg-white/10 size-9 rounded-full px-2" aria-label="Copy" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-md"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-ni7q5mnh.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button></div><div class="pt-3" style="transform: none;"><div class="relative z-0 flex max-w-full"><div id="code-block-viewer" dir="ltr" class="q9tKkq_viewer cm-editor z-10 light:cm-light dark:cm-light flex h-full w-full flex-col items-stretch ͼk ͼy"><div class="cm-scroller"><div class="cm-content q9tKkq_readonly"><span>MT4</span><br><span> │</span><br><span> ▼</span><br><span>PredictServer</span><br><span> │</span><br><span> ├── AI Engine (TensorFlow)</span><br><span> ├── Signal Engine</span><br><span> └── Risk Engine</span><br><span> │</span><br><span> ▼</span><br><span>PySide6 GUI</span></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=""><div class="" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"></div></div></div></div></div></pre>
<p data-start="2461" data-end="2512">So the GUI <strong data-start="2472" data-end="2511">doesn't run heavy ML logic directly</strong>.</p>
<hr data-start="2514" data-end="2517">
