" class="-ms-0.5 icon"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-ni7q5mnh.svg#6ef7a4" fill="currentColor"></use></svg>Run</div></button></div></div></div><div class="pointer-events-none absolute inset-x-4 top-12 bottom-4"><div class="pointer-events-none sticky z-40 shrink-0 z-1!" style="top: calc(calc(var(--sticky-padding-top) + 48px) - 1px * 3); margin-bottom: calc(-4px); height: calc(4px); mask-image: linear-gradient(transparent 25%, white 75%);"><div class="sticky bg-token-border-light" style="top: calc(var(--sticky-padding-top) + 48px); height: 1px;"></div></div></div><div class="" style="transform: none;"><div class="relative z-0 flex max-w-full"><div id="code-block-viewer" dir="ltr" class="q9tKkq_viewer cm-editor z-10 light:cm-light dark:cm-light flex h-full w-full flex-col items-stretch ͼk ͼy"><div class="cm-scroller"><div class="cm-content q9tKkq_readonly"><span class="ͼn">from</span><span> </span><span class="ͼt">lightgbm</span><span> </span><span class="ͼn">import</span><span> </span><span class="ͼt">LGBMClassifier</span></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=""><div class="" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"></div></div></div></div></div></pre>
<p data-start="1089" data-end="1097">Example:</p>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="1099" data-end="1266"><div class="relative w-full mt-4 mb-1"><div class=""><div class="relative"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"><div class="border border-token-border-light border-radius-3xl corner-superellipse/1.1 rounded-3xl"><div class="h-full w-full border-radius-3xl bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary corner-superellipse/1.1 overflow-clip rounded-3xl lxnfua_clipPathFallback"><div class="sticky z-2 select-none top-(--sticky-padding-top)"><div class="flex w-full items-center justify-between py-1.5 ps-4 pe-1.5 font-sans md:ps-5 bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary"><div class="flex max-w-[75%] min-w-0 cursor-default items-center text-sm font-medium justify-self-start text-token-text-primary"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-sm me-2.5 shrink-0"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-ni7q5mnh.svg#e45ab3" fill="currentColor"></use></svg>Python</div><div class="flex flex-row items-center gap-0.5 justify-self-end"><button class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none py-2 text-sm font-medium hover:bg-black/5 dark:hover:bg-white/10 size-9 rounded-full px-2" aria-label="Copy" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-md"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-ni7q5mnh.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button><button class="btn relative group-focus-within/dialog:focus-visible:[outline-width:1.5px] group-focus-within/dialog:focus-visible:[outline-offset:2.5px] group-focus-within/dialog:focus-visible:[outline-style:solid] group-focus-within/dialog:focus-visible:[outline-color:var(--text-primary)] btn-ghost border-token-border-default ms-2 border font-sans" aria-label="Run code" type="button"><div class="flex w-full items-center justify-center gap-1.5"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-label="" class="-ms-0.5 icon"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-ni7q5mnh.svg#6ef7a4" fill="currentColor"></use></svg>Run</div></button></div></div></div><div class="pointer-events-none absolute inset-x-4 top-12 bottom-4"><div class="pointer-events-none sticky z-40 shrink-0 z-1!" style="top: calc(calc(var(--sticky-padding-top) + 48px) - 1px * 3); margin-bottom: calc(-4px); height: calc(4px); mask-image: linear-gradient(transparent 25%, white 75%);"><div class="sticky bg-token-border-light" style="top: calc(var(--sticky-padding-top) + 48px); height: 1px;"></div></div></div><div class="" style="transform: none;"><div class="relative z-0 flex max-w-full"><div id="code-block-viewer" dir="ltr" class="q9tKkq_viewer cm-editor z-10 light:cm-light dark:cm-light flex h-full w-full flex-col items-stretch ͼk ͼy"><div class="cm-scroller"><div class="cm-content q9tKkq_readonly"><span class="ͼn">from</span><span> </span><span class="ͼt">lightgbm</span><span> </span><span class="ͼn">import</span><span> </span><span class="ͼt">LGBMClassifier</span><br><br><span class="ͼt">model</span><span> </span><span class="ͼn">=</span><span> </span><span class="ͼt">LGBMClassifier</span><span>(</span><br><span>    </span><span class="ͼt">n_estimators</span><span class="ͼn">=</span><span class="ͼq">300</span><span>,</span><br><span>    </span><span class="ͼt">learning_rate</span><span class="ͼn">=</span><span class="ͼq">0.05</span><span>,</span><br><span>    </span><span class="ͼt">max_depth</span><span class="ͼn">=</span><span class="ͼq">8</span><br><span>)</span><br><br><span class="ͼt">model</span><span class="ͼn">.</span><span>fit(</span><span class="ͼt">X_train</span><span>, </span><span class="ͼt">y_train</span><span>)</span></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=""><div class="" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"></div></div></div></div></div></pre>
<hr data-start="1268" data-end="1271">
<h1 data-section-id="17fysa7" data-start="1273" data-end="1330">⚡ Why These Are Better Than Neural Networks for Trading</h1>
<p data-start="1332" data-end="1366">Your MT4 features are things like:</p>
<ul data-start="1368" data-end="1430">
<li data-section-id="1o4t6o" data-start="1368" data-end="1373">
<p data-start="1370" data-end="1373">RSI</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1o4i9t" data-start="1374" data-end="1379">
<p data-start="1376" data-end="1379">EMA</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1j3yv8j" data-start="1380" data-end="1386">
<p data-start="1382" data-end="1386">MACD</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="16jlv51" data-start="1387" data-end="1394">
<p data-start="1389" data-end="1394">price</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="151te2i" data-start="1395" data-end="1410">
<p data-start="1397" data-end="1410">previous loss</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="5a58g4" data-start="1411" data-end="1430">
<p data-start="1413" data-end="1430">candle open/close</p>
</li>
</ul>
<p data-start="1432" data-end="1463">These are <strong data-start="1442" data-end="1462">tabular features</strong>.</p>
<p data-start="1465" data-end="1529">Neural networks (TensorFlow) are <strong data-start="1498" data-end="1511">not ideal</strong> for tabular data.</p>
<p data-start="1531" data-end="1588">Boosting models like <strong data-start="1552" data-end="1563">XGBoost</strong> usually outperform them.</p>
<div class="TyagGW_tableContainer"><div tabindex="-1" class="group TyagGW_tableWrapper flex flex-col-reverse w-fit"><table data-start="1590" data-end="1828" class="w-fit min-w-(--thread-content-width)"><thead data-start="1590" data-end="1630"><tr data-start="1590" data-end="1630"><th data-start="1590" data-end="1598" data-col-size="sm" class="">Model</th><th data-start="1598" data-end="1609" data-col-size="sm" class="">Accuracy</th><th data-start="1609" data-end="1617" data-col-size="sm" class="">Speed</th><th data-start="1617" data-end="1630" data-col-size="sm" class="">Stability</th></tr></thead><tbody data-start="1649" data-end="1828"><tr data-start="1649" data-end="1693"><td data-start="1649" data-end="1662" data-col-size="sm">RandomForest</td><td data-start="1662" data-end="1669" data-col-size="sm">good</td><td data-start="1669" data-end="1678" data-col-size="sm">medium</td><td data-start="1678" data-end="1693" data-col-size="sm">very stable</td></tr><tr data-start="1694" data-end="1737"><td data-start="1694" data-end="1702" data-col-size="sm">XGBoost</td><td data-start="1702" data-end="1718" data-col-size="sm"><strong data-start="1704" data-end="1717">excellent</strong></td><td data-start="1718" data-end="1727" data-col-size="sm">medium</td><td data-start="1727" data-end="1737" data-col-size="sm">stable</td></tr><tr data-start="1738" data-end="1780"><td data-start="1738" data-end="1747" data-col-size="sm">LightGBM</td><td data-start="1747" data-end="1759" data-col-size="sm">excellent</td><td data-start="1759" data-end="1770" data-col-size="sm"><strong data-start="1761" data-end="1769">fast</strong></td><td data-start="1770" data-end="1780" data-col-size="sm">stable</td></tr><tr data-start="1781" data-end="1828"><td data-start="1781" data-end="1795" data-col-size="sm">TensorFlow NN</td><td data-start="1795" data-end="1810" data-col-size="sm">inconsistent</td><td data-start="1810" data-end="1817" data-col-size="sm">slow</td><td data-start="1817" data-end="1828" data-col-size="sm">fragile</td></tr></tbody></table><div class="sticky h-0 select-none end-(--thread-content-margin) self-end"><div class="absolute end-0 flex items-end" style="height: 32.7969px;"><span class="" data-state="closed"><button aria-label="Copy table" class="hover:bg-token-bg-tertiary text-token-text-secondary my-1 rounded-sm p-1 transition-opacity group-[:not(:hover):not(:focus-within)]:pointer-events-none group-[:not(:hover):not(:focus-within)]:opacity-0"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-ni7q5mnh.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button></span></div></div></div></div>
<hr data-start="1830" data-end="1833">
<h1 data-section-id="ny2ycw" data-start="1835" data-end="1873">🧠 What I Recommend for Your Project</h1>
<p data-start="1875" data-end="1900">For <strong data-start="1879" data-end="1899">Mt4PredictServer</strong>:</p>
<p data-start="1902" data-end="1918">Use <strong data-start="1906" data-end="1917">XGBoost</strong>.</p>
<p data-start="1920" data-end="1946">Example training pipeline:</p>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="1948" data-end="2063"><div class="relative w-full mt-4 mb-1"><div class=""><div class="relative"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"><div class="border border-token-border-light border-radius-3xl corner-superellipse/1.1 rounded-3xl"><div class="h-full w-full border-radius-3xl bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary corner-superellipse/1.1 overflow-clip rounded-3xl lxnfua_clipPathFallback"><div class="pointer-events-none absolute end-1.5 top-1 z-2 md:end-2 md:top-1"><button class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none pointer-events-auto py-2 text-sm font-medium hover:bg-black/5 dark:hover:bg-white/10 size-9 rounded-full px-2" aria-label="Copy" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-md"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-ni7q5mnh.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button></div><div class="pt-3" style="transform: none;"><div class="relative z-0 flex max-w-full"><div id="code-block-viewer" dir="ltr" class="q9tKkq_viewer cm-editor z-10 light:cm-light dark:cm-light flex h-full w-full flex-col items-stretch ͼk ͼy"><div class="cm-scroller"><div class="cm-content q9tKkq_readonly"><span>MT4 data</span><br><span>   ↓</span><br><span>feature builder</span><br><span>   ↓</span><br><span>XGBoost model</span><br><span>   ↓</span><br><span>prediction (BUY / SELL probability)</span><br><span>   ↓</span><br><span>trade signal</span></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=""><div class="" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"></div></div></div></div></div></pre>
<p data-start="2065" data-end="2126">This is exactly how many <strong data-start="2090" data-end="2125">quant funds build signal models</strong>.</p>
<hr data-start="2128" data-end="2131">
