p-hover/turn-messages:opacity-100 group-focus-within/turn-messages:pointer-events-auto group-focus-within/turn-messages:opacity-100 has-data-[state=open]:pointer-events-auto has-data-[state=open]:opacity-100" style="mask-position: 0% 0%;"><button class="text-token-text-secondary hover:bg-token-bg-secondary rounded-lg" aria-label="Copy" aria-pressed="false" data-testid="copy-turn-action-button" data-state="closed"><span class="flex items-center justify-center touch:w-10 h-8 w-8"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-ni7q5mnh.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></span></button><button class="text-token-text-secondary hover:bg-token-bg-secondary rounded-lg" aria-label="Edit message" aria-pressed="false" data-state="closed"><span class="flex items-center justify-center touch:w-10 h-8 w-8"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-ni7q5mnh.svg#6d87e1" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></span></button></div></div></div></div><span class="sr-only"><br></span></article><article class="text-token-text-primary w-full focus:outline-none [--shadow-height:45px] has-data-writing-block:pointer-events-none has-data-writing-block:-mt-(--shadow-height) has-data-writing-block:pt-(--shadow-height) [&amp;:has([data-writing-block])&gt;*]:pointer-events-auto scroll-mt-[calc(var(--header-height)+min(200px,max(70px,20svh)))]" tabindex="-1" dir="auto" data-turn-id="0efc9c20-0c79-45e9-b47b-a8950e5c68a2" data-testid="conversation-turn-24" data-scroll-anchor="false" data-turn="assistant"><h6 class="sr-only select-none">ChatGPT said:</h6><div class="text-base my-auto mx-auto [--thread-content-margin:var(--thread-content-margin-xs,calc(var(--spacing)*4))] @w-sm/main:[--thread-content-margin:var(--thread-content-margin-sm,calc(var(--spacing)*6))] @w-lg/main:[--thread-content-margin:var(--thread-content-margin-lg,calc(var(--spacing)*16))] px-(--thread-content-margin)"><div tabindex="-1" class="[--thread-content-max-width:40rem] @w-lg/main:[--thread-content-max-width:48rem] mx-auto max-w-(--thread-content-max-width) flex-1 group/turn-messages focus-visible:outline-hidden relative flex w-full min-w-0 flex-col agent-turn"><div class="flex max-w-full flex-col gap-4 grow"><div data-message-author-role="assistant" data-message-id="0efc9c20-0c79-45e9-b47b-a8950e5c68a2" dir="auto" data-message-model-slug="gpt-5-3-instant" class="min-h-8 text-message relative flex w-full flex-col items-end gap-2 text-start break-words whitespace-normal [.text-message+&amp;]:mt-1"><div class="flex w-full flex-col gap-1 empty:hidden"><div class="markdown prose dark:prose-invert w-full wrap-break-word dark markdown-new-styling"><p data-start="0" data-end="203">Great idea. A <strong data-start="14" data-end="30">Risk Manager</strong> is one of the most important components in a trading system. It sits between the <strong data-start="112" data-end="125">AI signal</strong> and the <strong data-start="134" data-end="153">trade execution</strong> to prevent dangerous trades and control exposure.</p>
<p data-start="205" data-end="280">For your <strong data-start="214" data-end="247">Mt4PredictServer architecture</strong>, the risk manager should handle:</p>
<ul data-start="282" data-end="492">
<li data-section-id="yzfrdd" data-start="282" data-end="301">
<p data-start="284" data-end="301">position sizing</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="xs1xzy" data-start="302" data-end="324">
<p data-start="304" data-end="324">max risk per trade</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1ju7ngh" data-start="325" data-end="347">
<p data-start="327" data-end="347">portfolio exposure</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="lwe3y1" data-start="348" data-end="371">
<p data-start="350" data-end="371">drawdown protection</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1ufgqaq" data-start="372" data-end="414">
<p data-start="374" data-end="414">trade blocking when conditions are bad</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1wxuvff" data-start="415" data-end="462">
<p data-start="417" data-end="462">dynamic stop-loss / take-profit suggestions</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="11obae1" data-start="463" data-end="492">
<p data-start="465" data-end="492">account health monitoring</p>
</li>
</ul>
<p data-start="494" data-end="575">Below is a <strong data-start="505" data-end="535">complete <code data-start="516" data-end="533">risk_manager.py</code></strong> designed to integrate with your system.</p>
<hr data-start="577" data-end="580">
<h1 data-section-id="h4tlt" data-start="582" data-end="633">risk_manager.py (Institutional-style Risk Engine)</h1>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="635" data-end="6619"><div class="relative w-full mt-4 mb-1"><div class=""><div class="relative"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"><div class="border border-token-border-light border-radius-3xl corner-superellipse/1.1 rounded-3xl"><div class="h-full w-full border-radius-3xl bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary corner-superellipse/1.1 overflow-clip rounded-3xl lxnfua_clipPathFallback"><div class="sticky z-2 select-none top-(--sticky-padding-top)"><div class="flex w-full items-center justify-between py-1.5 ps-4 pe-1.5 font-sans md:ps-5 bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary"><div class="flex max-w-[75%] min-w-0 cursor-default items-center text-sm font-medium justify-self-start text-token-text-primary"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-sm me-2.5 shrink-0"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-ni7q5mnh.svg#e45ab3" fill="currentColor"></use></svg>Python</div><div class="flex flex-row items-center gap-0.5 justify-self-end"><button class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none py-2 text-sm font-medium hover:bg-black/5 dark:hover:bg-white/10 size-9 rounded-full px-2" aria-label="Copy" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-md"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-ni7q5mnh.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button><button class="btn relative group-focus-within/dialog:focus-visible:[outline-width:1.5px] group-focus-within/dialog:focus-visible:[outline-offset:2.5px] group-focus-within/dialog:focus-visible:[outline-style:solid] group-focus-within/dialog:focus-visible:[outline-color:var(--text-primary)] btn-ghost border-token-border-default ms-2 border font-sans" aria-label="Run code" type="button"><div class="flex w-full items-center justify-center gap-1.5"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-label="" class="-ms-0.5 icon"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-ni7q5mnh.svg#6ef7a4" fill="currentColor"></use></svg>Run</div></button></div></div></div><div class="pointer-events-none absolute inset-x-4 top-12 bottom-4"><div class="pointer-events-none sticky z-40 shrink-0 z-1!" style="top: calc(calc(var(--sticky-padding-top) + 48px) - 1px * 3); margin-bottom: calc(-4px); height: calc(4px); mask-image: linear-gradient(transparent 25%, white 75%);"><div class="sticky bg-token-border-light" style="top: calc(var(--sticky-padding-top) + 48px); height: 1px;"></div></div></div><div class="" style="transform: none;"><div class="relative z-0 flex max-w-full"><div id="code-block-viewer" dir="ltr" class="q9tKkq_viewer cm-editor z-10 light:cm-light dark:cm-light flex h-full w-full flex-col items-stretch ͼk ͼy"><div class="cm-scroller"><div class="cm-content q9tKkq_readonly"><span class="ͼr">"""</span><br><span class="ͼr">===============================================================</span><br><span class="ͼr">🛡 RiskManager — Trade Risk Control Layer</span><br><span class="ͼr">---------------------------------------------------------------</span><br><span class="ͼr">Protects the account by controlling exposure, drawdown,</span><br><span class="ͼr">and position sizing before a trade is executed.</span><br><span class="ͼr">===============================================================</span><br><span class="ͼr">"""</span><br><br><span class="ͼn">import</span><span> </span><span class="ͼt">os</span><br><span class="ͼn">import</span><span> </span><span class="ͼt">time</span><br><span class="ͼn">import</span><span> </span><span class="ͼt">pandas</span><span> </span><span class="ͼn">as</span><span> </span><span class="ͼt">pd</span><br><br><br><span class="ͼn">class</span><span> </span><span class="ͼs">RiskManager</span><span>:</span><br><br><span>    </span><span class="ͼn">def</span><span> </span><span class="ͼt">__init__</span><span>(</span><span class="ͼt">self</span><span>, </span><span class="ͼt">controller</span><span class="ͼn">=</span><span class="ͼq">None</span><span>):</span><br><br><span>        </span><span class="ͼt">self</span><span class="ͼn">.</span><span>controller </span><span class="ͼn">=</span><span> </span><span class="ͼt">controller</span><br><br><span>        </span><span class="ͼt">self</span><span class="ͼn">.</span><span>max_risk_per_trade </span><span class="ͼn">=</span><span> </span><span class="ͼq">0.02</span><span>      </span><span class="ͼl"># 2%</span><br><span>        </span><span class="ͼt">self</span><span class="ͼn">.</span><span>max_account_risk </span><span class="ͼn">=</span><span> </span><span class="ͼq">0.10</span><span>        </span><span class="ͼl"># 10%</span><br><span>        </span><span class="ͼt">self</span><span class="ͼn">.</span><span>max_open_positions </span><span class="ͼn">=</span><span> </span><span class="ͼq">6</span><br><span>        </span><span class="ͼt">self</span><span class="ͼn">.</span><span>max_drawdown </span><span class="ͼn">=</span><span> </span><span class="ͼq">0.25</span><span>            </span><span class="ͼl"># 25%</span><br><br><span>        </span><span class="ͼt">self</span><span class="ͼn">.</span><span>order_history_path </span><span class="ͼn">=</span><span> </span><span class="ͼr">"./src/data/order_history.csv"</span><br><br><span>        </span><span class="ͼn">if</span><span> </span><span class="ͼt">self</span><span class="ͼn">.</span><span>controller </span><span class="ͼn">and</span><span> </span><span class="ͼt">hasattr</span><span>(</span><span class="ͼt">self</span><span class="ͼn">.</span><span>controller, </span><span class="ͼr">"logger"</span><span>):</span><br><span>            </span><span class="ͼt">self</span><span class="ͼn">.</span><span>logger </span><span class="ͼn">=</span><span> </span><span class="ͼt">self</span><span class="ͼn">.</span><span>controller</span><span class="ͼn">.</span><span>logger</span><br><span>        </span><span class="ͼn">else</span><span>:</span><br><span>            </span><span class="ͼn">import</span><span> </span><span class="ͼt">logging</span><br><span>            </span><span class="ͼt">logging</span><span class="ͼn">.</span><span>basicConfig(</span><span class="ͼt">level</span><span class="ͼn">=</span><span class="ͼt">logging</span><span class="ͼn">.</span><span>INFO)</span><br><span>            </span><span class="ͼt">self</span><span class="ͼn">.</span><span>logger </span><span class="ͼn">=</span><span> </span><span class="ͼt">logging</span><span class="ͼn">.</span><span>getLogger(</span><span class="ͼr">"RiskManager"</span><span>)</span><br><br><span>    </span><span class="ͼl"># ----------------------------------------------------------</span><br><span>    </span><span class="ͼl"># MAIN VALIDATION</span><br><span>    </span><span class="ͼl"># ----------------------------------------------------------</span><br><span>    </span><span class="ͼn">def</span><span> </span><span class="ͼt">validate_trade</span><span>(</span><span class="ͼt">self</span><span>, </span><span class="ͼt">signal</span><span>, </span><span class="ͼt">account_state</span><span>):</span><br><br><span>        </span><span class="ͼr">"""</span><br><span class="ͼr">        Check if a trade should be allowed.</span><br><span class="ͼr">        """</span><br><br><span>        </span><span class="ͼn">try</span><span>:</span><br><br><span>            </span><span class="ͼt">risk</span><span> </span><span class="ͼn">=</span><span> </span><span class="ͼt">self</span><span class="ͼn">.</span><span>_compute_portfolio_risk(</span><span class="ͼt">account_state</span><span>)</span><br><br><span>            </span><span class="ͼn">if</span><span> </span><span class="ͼt">risk</span><span> </span><span class="ͼn">&gt;</span><span> </span><span class="ͼt">self</span><span class="ͼn">.</span><span>max_account_risk:</span><br><span>                </span><span class="ͼn">return</span><span> {</span><br><span>                    </span><span class="ͼr">"allowed"</span><span>: </span><span class="ͼq">False</span><span>,</span><br><span>                    </span><span class="ͼr">"reason"</span><span>: </span><span class="ͼr">"Portfolio risk limit exceeded"</span><br><span>                }</span><br><br><span>            </span><span class="ͼn">if</span><span> </span><span class="ͼt">account_state</span><span class="ͼn">.</span><span>get(</span><span class="ͼr">"open_positions"</span><span>, </span><span class="ͼq">0</span><span>) </span><span class="ͼn">&gt;=</span><span> </span><span class="ͼt">self</span><span class="ͼn">.</span><span>max_open_positions:</span><br><span>                </span><span class="ͼn">return</span><span> {</span><br><span>                    </span><span class="ͼr">"allowed"</span><span>: </span><span class="ͼq">False</span><span>,</span><br><span>                    </span><span class="ͼr">"reason"</span><span>: </span><span class="ͼr">"Too many open positions"</span><br><span>                }</span><br><br><span>            </span><span class="ͼn">if</span><span> </span><span class="ͼt">self</span><span class="ͼn">.</span><span>_check_drawdown(</span><span class="ͼt">account_state</span><span>):</span><br><span>                </span><span class="ͼn">return</span><span> {</span><br><span>                    </span><span class="ͼr">"allowed"</span><span>: </span><span class="ͼq">False</span><span>,</span><br><span>                    </span><span class="ͼr">"reason"</span><span>: </span><span class="ͼr">"Account drawdown limit reached"</span><br><span>                }</span><br><br><span>            </span><span class="ͼn">return</span><span> {</span><span class="ͼr">"allowed"</span><span>: </span><span class="ͼq">True</span><span>}</span><br><br><span>        </span><span class="ͼn">except</span><span> </span><span class="ͼt">Exception</span><span> </span><span class="ͼn">as</span><span> </span><span class="ͼt">e</span><span>:</span><br><br><span>            </span><span class="ͼt">self</span><span class="ͼn">.</span><span>logger</span><span class="ͼn">.</span><span>error(</span><span class="ͼr">f"Risk validation error: </span><span>{</span><span class="ͼt">e</span><span>}</span><span class="ͼr">"</span><span>)</span><br><br><span>            </span><span class="ͼn">return</span><span> {</span><br><span>                </span><span class="ͼr">"allowed"</span><span>: </span><span class="ͼq">False</span><span>,</span><br><span>                </span><span class="ͼr">"reason"</span><span>: </span><span class="ͼr">"Risk validation failure"</span><br><span>            }</span><br><br><span>    </span><span class="ͼl"># ----------------------------------------------------------</span><br><span>    </span><span class="ͼl"># POSITION SIZE</span><br><span>    </span><span class="ͼl"># ----------------------------------------------------------</span><br><span>    </span><span class="ͼn">def</span><span> </span><span class="ͼt">compute_position_size</span><span>(</span><span class="ͼt">self</span><span>, </span><span class="ͼt">balance</span><span>, </span><span class="ͼt">stop_loss_pips</span><span>, </span><span class="ͼt">pip_value</span><span class="ͼn">=</span><span class="ͼq">10</span><span>):</span><br><br><span>        </span><span class="ͼr">"""</span><br><span class="ͼr">        Calculate lot size using risk percentage.</span><br><span class="ͼr">        """</span><br><br><span>        </span><span class="ͼn">try</span><span>:</span><br><br><span>            </span><span class="ͼt">risk_amount</span><span> </span><span class="ͼn">=</span><span> </span><span class="ͼt">balance</span><span> </span><span class="ͼn">*</span><span> </span><span class="ͼt">self</span><span class="ͼn">.</span><span>max_risk_per_trade</span><br><br><span>            </span><span class="ͼn">if</span><span> </span><span class="ͼt">stop_loss_pips</span><span> </span><span class="ͼn">&lt;=</span><span> </span><span class="ͼq">0</span><span>:</span><br><span>                </span><span class="ͼn">return</span><span> </span><span class="ͼq">0</span><br><br><span>            </span><span class="ͼt">lot_size</span><span> </span><span class="ͼn">=</span><span> </span><span class="ͼt">risk_amount</span><span> </span><span class="ͼn">/</span><span> (</span><span class="ͼt">stop_loss_pips</span><span> </span><span class="ͼn">*</span><span> </span><span class="ͼt">pip_value</span><span>)</span><br><br><span>            </span><span class="ͼn">return</span><span> </span><span class="ͼt">round</span><span>(</span><span class="ͼt">lot_size</span><span>, </span><span class="ͼq">3</span><span>)</span><br><br><span>        </span><span class="ͼn">except</span><span> </span><span class="ͼt">Exception</span><span> </span><span class="ͼn">as</span><span> </span><span class="ͼt">e</span><span>:</span><br><br><span>            </span><span class="ͼt">self</span><span class="ͼn">.</span><span>logger</span><span class="ͼn">.</span><span>error(</span><span class="ͼr">f"Position size error: </span><span>{</span><span class="ͼt">e</span><span>}</span><span class="ͼr">"</span><span>)</span><br><br><span>            </span><span class="ͼn">return</span><span> </span><span class="ͼq">0</span><br><br><span>    </span><span class="ͼl"># ----------------------------------------------------------</span><br><span>    </span><span class="ͼl"># PORTFOLIO RISK</span><br><span>    </span><span class="ͼl"># ----------------------------------------------------------</span><br><span>    </span><span class="ͼn">def</span><span> </span><span class="ͼt">_compute_portfolio_risk</span><span>(</span><span class="ͼt">self</span><span>, </span><span class="ͼt">account_state</span><span>):</span><br><br><span>        </span><span class="ͼr">"""</span><br><span class="ͼr">        Estimate total risk exposure.</span><br><span class="ͼr">        """</span><br><br><span>        </span><span class="ͼt">balance</span><span> </span><span class="ͼn">=</span><span> </span><span class="ͼt">account_state</span><span class="ͼn">.</span><span>get(</span><span class="ͼr">"balance"</span><span>, </span><span class="ͼq">0</span><span>)</span><br><span>        </span><span class="ͼt">equity</span><span> </span><span class="ͼn">=</span><span> </span><span class="ͼt">account_state</span><span class="ͼn">.</span><span>get(</span><span class="ͼr">"equity"</span><span>, </span><span class="ͼt">balance</span><span>)</span><br><br><span>        </span><span class="ͼn">if</span><span> </span><span class="ͼt">balance</span><span> </span><span class="ͼn">==</span><span> </span><span class="ͼq">0</span><span>:</span><br><span>            </span><span class="ͼn">return</span><span> </span><span class="ͼq">0</span><br><br><span>        </span><span class="ͼt">drawdown</span><span> </span><span class="ͼn">=</span><span> (</span><span class="ͼt">balance</span><span> </span><span class="ͼn">-</span><span> </span><span class="ͼt">equity</span><span>) </span><span class="ͼn">/</span><span> </span><span class="ͼt">balance</span><br><br><span>        </span><span class="ͼn">return</span><span> </span><span class="ͼt">max</span><span>(</span><span class="ͼt">drawdown</span><span>, </span><span class="ͼq">0</span><span>)</span><br><br><span>    </span><span class="ͼl"># ----------------------------------------------------------</span><br><span>    </span><span class="ͼl"># DRAWDOWN CHECK</span><br><span>    </span><span class="ͼl"># ----------------------------------------------------------</span><br><span>    </span><span class="ͼn">def</span><span> </span><span class="ͼt">_check_drawdown</span><span>(</span><span class="ͼt">self</span><span>, </span><span class="ͼt">account_state</span><span>):</span><br><br><span>        </span><span class="ͼt">balance</span><span> </span><span class="ͼn">=</span><span> </span><span class="ͼt">account_state</span><span class="ͼn">.</span><span>get(</span><span class="ͼr">"balance"</span><span>, </span><span class="ͼq">0</span><span>)</span><br><span>        </span><span class="ͼt">equity</span><span> </span><span class="ͼn">=</span><span> </span><span class="ͼt">account_state</span><span class="ͼn">.</span><span>get(</span><span class="ͼr">"equity"</span><span>, </span><span class="ͼt">balance</span><span>)</span><br><br><span>        </span><span class="ͼn">if</span><span> </span><span class="ͼt">balance</span><span> </span><span class="ͼn">==</span><span> </span><span class="ͼq">0</span><span>:</span><br><span>            </span><span class="ͼn">return</span><span> </span><span class="ͼq">False</span><br><br><span>        </span><span class="ͼt">drawdown</span><span> </span><span class="ͼn">=</span><span> (</span><span class="ͼt">balance</span><span> </span><span class="ͼn">-</span><span> </span><span class="ͼt">equity</span><span>) </span><span class="ͼn">/</span><span> </span><span class="ͼt">balance</span><br><br><span>        </span><span class="ͼn">if</span><span> </span><span class="ͼt">drawdown</span><span> </span><span class="ͼn">&gt;</span><span> </span><span class="ͼt">self</span><span class="ͼn">.</span><span>max_drawdown:</span><br><br><span>            </span><span class="ͼt">self</span><span class="ͼn">.</span><span>logger</span><span class="ͼn">.</span><span>warning(</span><br><span>                </span><span class="ͼr">f"⚠ Drawdown limit exceeded (</span><span>{</span><span class="ͼt">round</span><span>(</span><span class="ͼt">drawdown</span><span class="ͼn">*</span><span class="ͼq">100</span><span>,</span><span class="ͼq">2</span><span>)}</span><span class="ͼr">%)"</span><br><span>            )</span><br><br><span>            </span><span class="ͼn">return</span><span> </span><span class="ͼq">True</span><br><br><span>        </span><span class="ͼn">return</span><span> </span><span class="ͼq">False</span><br><br><span>    </span><span class="ͼl"># ----------------------------------------------------------</span><br><span>    </span><span class="ͼl"># STOP LOSS / TAKE PROFIT SUGGESTION</span><br><span>    </span><span class="ͼl"># ----------------------------------------------------------</span><br><span>    </span><span class="ͼn">def</span><span> </span><span class="ͼt">suggest_trade_levels</span><span>(</span><span class="ͼt">self</span><span>, </span><span class="ͼt">price</span><span>, </span><span class="ͼt">atr</span><span>):</span><br><br><span>        </span><span class="ͼr">"""</span><br><span class="ͼr">        Suggest stop loss and take profit using ATR.</span><br><span class="ͼr">        """</span><br><br><span>        </span><span class="ͼn">try</span><span>:</span><br><br><span>            </span><span class="ͼt">stop_loss</span><span> </span><span class="ͼn">=</span><span> </span><span class="ͼt">price</span><span> </span><span class="ͼn">-</span><span> (</span><span class="ͼt">atr</span><span> </span><span class="ͼn">*</span><span> </span><span class="ͼq">1.5</span><span>)</span><br><span>            </span><span class="ͼt">take_profit</span><span> </span><span class="ͼn">=</span><span> </span><span class="ͼt">price</span><span> </span><span class="ͼn">+</span><span> (</span><span class="ͼt">atr</span><span> </span><span class="ͼn">*</span><span> </span><span class="ͼq">3</span><span>)</span><br><br><span>            </span><span class="ͼn">return</span><span> {</span><br><span>                </span><span class="ͼr">"stop_loss"</span><span>: </span><span class="ͼt">round</span><span>(</span><span class="ͼt">stop_loss</span><span>, </span><span class="ͼq">5</span><span>),</span><br><span>                </span><span class="ͼr">"take_profit"</span><span>: </span><span class="ͼt">round</span><span>(</span><span class="ͼt">take_profit</span><span>, </span><span class="ͼq">5</span><span>)</span><br><span>            }</span><br><br><span>        </span><span class="ͼn">except</span><span>:</span><br><br><span>            </span><span class="ͼn">return</span><span> </span><span class="ͼq">None</span><br><br><span>    </span><span class="ͼl"># ----------------------------------------------------------</span><br><span>    </span><span class="ͼl"># TRADE HISTORY ANALYSIS</span><br><span>    </span><span class="ͼl"># ----------------------------------------------------------</span><br><span>    </span><span class="ͼn">def</span><span> </span><span class="ͼt">get_recent_performance</span><span>(</span><span class="ͼt">self</span><span>, </span><span class="ͼt">last_n</span><span class="ͼn">=</span><span class="ͼq">20</span><span>):</span><br><br><span>        </span><span class="ͼn">try</span><span>:</span><br><br><span>            </span><span class="ͼn">if</span><span> </span><span class="ͼn">not</span><span> </span><span class="ͼt">os</span><span class="ͼn">.</span><span>path</span><span class="ͼn">.</span><span>exists(</span><span class="ͼt">self</span><span class="ͼn">.</span><span>order_history_path):</span><br><span>                </span><span class="ͼn">return</span><span> </span><span class="ͼq">None</span><br><br><span>            </span><span class="ͼt">df</span><span> </span><span class="ͼn">=</span><span> </span><span class="ͼt">pd</span><span class="ͼn">.</span><span>read_csv(</span><span class="ͼt">self</span><span class="ͼn">.</span><span>order_history_path)</span><br><br><span>            </span><span class="ͼn">if</span><span> </span><span class="ͼt">df</span><span class="ͼn">.</span><span>empty </span><span class="ͼn">or</span><span> </span><span class="ͼr">"profit"</span><span> </span><span class="ͼn">not</span><span> </span><span class="ͼn">in</span><span> </span><span class="ͼt">df</span><span class="ͼn">.</span><span>columns:</span><br><span>                </span><span class="ͼn">return</span><span> </span><span class="ͼq">None</span><br><br><span>            </span><span class="ͼt">recent</span><span> </span><span class="ͼn">=</span><span> </span><span class="ͼt">df</span><span class="ͼn">.</span><span>tail(</span><span class="ͼt">last_n</span><span>)</span><br><br><span>            </span><span class="ͼt">wins</span><span> </span><span class="ͼn">=</span><span> </span><span class="ͼt">len</span><span>(</span><span class="ͼt">recent</span><span>[</span><span class="ͼt">recent</span><span>[</span><span class="ͼr">"profit"</span><span>] </span><span class="ͼn">&gt;</span><span> </span><span class="ͼq">0</span><span>])</span><br><span>            </span><span class="ͼt">losses</span><span> </span><span class="ͼn">=</span><span> </span><span class="ͼt">len</span><span>(</span><span class="ͼt">recent</span><span>[</span><span class="ͼt">recent</span><span>[</span><span class="ͼr">"profit"</span><span>] </span><span class="ͼn">&lt;=</span><span> </span><span class="ͼq">0</span><span>])</span><br><br><span>            </span><span class="ͼt">win_rate</span><span> </span><span class="ͼn">=</span><span> </span><span class="ͼt">wins</span><span> </span><span class="ͼn">/</span><span> </span><span class="ͼt">max</span><span>((</span><span class="ͼt">wins</span><span> </span><span class="ͼn">+</span><span> </span><span class="ͼt">losses</span><span>), </span><span class="ͼq">1</span><span>)</span><br><br><span>            </span><span class="ͼn">return</span><span> {</span><br><span>                </span><span class="ͼr">"wins"</span><span>: </span><span class="ͼt">wins</span><span>,</span><br><span>                </span><span class="ͼr">"losses"</span><span>: </span><span class="ͼt">losses</span><span>,</span><br><span>                </span><span class="ͼr">"win_rate"</span><span>: </span><span class="ͼt">round</span><span>(</span><span class="ͼt">win_rate</span><span>, </span><span class="ͼq">3</span><span>)</span><br><span>            }</span><br><br><span>        </span><span class="ͼn">except</span><span> </span><span class="ͼt">Exception</span><span> </span><span class="ͼn">as</span><span> </span><span class="ͼt">e</span><span>:</span><br><br><span>            </span><span class="ͼt">self</span><span class="ͼn">.</span><span>logger</span><span class="ͼn">.</span><span>error(</span><span class="ͼr">f"Performance analysis error: </span><span>{</span><span class="ͼt">e</span><span>}</span><span class="ͼr">"</span><span>)</span><br><br><span>            </span><span class="ͼn">return</span><span> </span><span class="ͼq">None</span><br><br><span>    </span><span class="ͼl"># ----------------------------------------------------------</span><br><span>    </span><span class="ͼl"># TRADE COOLDOWN</span><br><span>    </span><span class="ͼl"># ----------------------------------------------------------</span><br><span>    </span><span class="ͼn">def</span><span> </span><span class="ͼt">enforce_trade_cooldown</span><span>(</span><span class="ͼt">self</span><span>, </span><span class="ͼt">last_trade_time</span><span>, </span><span class="ͼt">cooldown_sec</span><span class="ͼn">=</span><span class="ͼq">10</span><span>):</span><br><br><span>        </span><span class="ͼt">now</span><span> </span><span class="ͼn">=</span><span> </span><span class="ͼt">time</span><span class="ͼn">.</span><span>time()</span><br><br><span>        </span><span class="ͼn">if</span><span> </span><span class="ͼt">last_trade_time</span><span> </span><span class="ͼn">is</span><span> </span><span class="ͼq">None</span><span>:</span><br><span>            </span><span class="ͼn">return</span><span> </span><span class="ͼq">True</span><br><br><span>        </span><span class="ͼn">if</span><span> </span><span class="ͼt">now</span><span> </span><span class="ͼn">-</span><span> </span><span class="ͼt">last_trade_time</span><span> </span><span class="ͼn">&lt;</span><span> </span><span class="ͼt">cooldown_sec</span><span>:</span><br><br><span>            </span><span class="ͼt">self</span><span class="ͼn">.</span><span>logger</span><span class="ͼn">.</span><span>info(</span><span class="ͼr">"⏳ Trade cooldown active"</span><span>)</span><br><br><span>            </span><span class="ͼn">return</span><span> </span><span class="ͼq">False</span><br><br><span>        </span><span class="ͼn">return</span><span> </span><span class="ͼq">True</span></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=""><div class="" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"></div></div></div></div></div></pre>
