<p data-start="248" data-end="273">But your new system uses:</p>
<ul data-start="275" data-end="327">
<li data-section-id="1t66ej6" data-start="275" data-end="288">
<p data-start="277" data-end="288"><strong data-start="277" data-end="288">XGBoost</strong></p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="15lzvge" data-start="289" data-end="307">
<p data-start="291" data-end="307"><strong data-start="291" data-end="307">Scikit-learn</strong></p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1rf1n4k" data-start="308" data-end="327">
<p data-start="310" data-end="327"><strong data-start="310" data-end="327">joblib models</strong></p>
</li>
</ul>
<p data-start="329" data-end="444">So the metrics viewer should evolve into a <strong data-start="372" data-end="413">general AI Training Metrics Dashboard</strong>, not a TensorFlow-only viewer.</p>
<p data-start="446" data-end="498">I’ll give you an <strong data-start="463" data-end="483">upgraded version</strong> that supports:</p>
<h3 data-section-id="19xjzik" data-start="500" data-end="520">New capabilities</h3>
<ul data-start="521" data-end="824">
<li data-section-id="veero5" data-start="521" data-end="551">
<p data-start="523" data-end="551">Works <strong data-start="529" data-end="551">without TensorFlow</strong></p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="e76auw" data-start="552" data-end="584">
<p data-start="554" data-end="584">Reads <strong data-start="560" data-end="584">training metrics CSV</strong></p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1d2b5vc" data-start="585" data-end="615">
<p data-start="587" data-end="615">Supports <strong data-start="596" data-end="615">multiple models</strong></p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="nljq67" data-start="616" data-end="643">
<p data-start="618" data-end="643">Supports <strong data-start="627" data-end="643">live refresh</strong></p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1naf0wk" data-start="644" data-end="682">
<p data-start="646" data-end="682">Shows <strong data-start="652" data-end="682">accuracy / loss / win rate</strong></p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1npp2zk" data-start="683" data-end="731">
<p data-start="685" data-end="731">Can still read <strong data-start="700" data-end="731">TensorBoard logs if present</strong></p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="pd21k6" data-start="732" data-end="765">
<p data-start="734" data-end="765">Adds <strong data-start="739" data-end="765">model statistics panel</strong></p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1b1mvtp" data-start="766" data-end="790">
<p data-start="768" data-end="790">Adds <strong data-start="773" data-end="790">reload button</strong></p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="12hyi8k" data-start="791" data-end="824">
<p data-start="793" data-end="824">Adds <strong data-start="798" data-end="824">training history chart</strong></p>
</li>
</ul>
<hr data-start="826" data-end="829">
<h1 data-section-id="12zchoa" data-start="831" data-end="856">Upgraded AI Metrics Tab</h1>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="858" data-end="6210"><div class="relative w-full mt-4 mb-1"><div class=""><div class="relative"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"><div class="border border-token-border-light border-radius-3xl corner-superellipse/1.1 rounded-3xl"><div class="h-full w-full border-radius-3xl bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary corner-superellipse/1.1 overflow-clip rounded-3xl lxnfua_clipPathFallback"><div class="sticky z-2 select-none top-(--sticky-padding-top)"><div class="flex w-full items-center justify-between py-1.5 ps-4 pe-1.5 font-sans md:ps-5 bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary"><div class="flex max-w-[75%] min-w-0 cursor-default items-center text-sm font-medium justify-self-start text-token-text-primary"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-sm me-2.5 shrink-0"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-ni7q5mnh.svg#e45ab3" fill="currentColor"></use></svg>Python</div><div class="flex flex-row items-center gap-0.5 justify-self-end"><button class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none py-2 text-sm font-medium hover:bg-black/5 dark:hover:bg-white/10 size-9 rounded-full px-2" aria-label="Copy" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-md"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-ni7q5mnh.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button><button class="btn relative group-focus-within/dialog:focus-visible:[outline-width:1.5px] group-focus-within/dialog:focus-visible:[outline-offset:2.5px] group-focus-within/dialog:focus-visible:[outline-style:solid] group-focus-within/dialog:focus-visible:[outline-color:var(--text-primary)] btn-ghost border-token-border-default ms-2 border font-sans" aria-label="Run code" type="button"><div class="flex w-full items-center justify-center gap-1.5"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-label="" class="-ms-0.5 icon"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-ni7q5mnh.svg#6ef7a4" fill="currentColor"></use></svg>Run</div></button></div></div></div><div class="pointer-events-none absolute inset-x-4 top-12 bottom-4"><div class="pointer-events-none sticky z-40 shrink-0 z-1!" style="top: calc(calc(var(--sticky-padding-top) + 48px) - 1px * 3); margin-bottom: calc(-4px); height: calc(4px); mask-image: linear-gradient(transparent 25%, white 75%);"><div class="sticky bg-token-border-light" style="top: calc(var(--sticky-padding-top) + 48px); height: 1px;"></div></div></div><div class="" style="transform: none;"><div class="relative z-0 flex max-w-full"><div id="code-block-viewer" dir="ltr" class="q9tKkq_viewer cm-editor z-10 light:cm-light dark:cm-light flex h-full w-full flex-col items-stretch ͼk ͼy"><div class="cm-scroller"><div class="cm-content q9tKkq_readonly"><span class="ͼn">import</span><span> </span><span class="ͼt">logging</span><br><span class="ͼn">import</span><span> </span><span class="ͼt">os</span><br><span class="ͼn">from</span><span> </span><span class="ͼt">pathlib</span><span> </span><span class="ͼn">import</span><span> </span><span class="ͼt">Path</span><br><br><span class="ͼn">from</span><span> </span><span class="ͼt">PySide6</span><span class="ͼn">.</span><span class="ͼt">QtCore</span><span> </span><span class="ͼn">import</span><span> </span><span class="ͼt">Qt</span><br><span class="ͼn">from</span><span> </span><span class="ͼt">PySide6</span><span class="ͼn">.</span><span class="ͼt">QtGui</span><span> </span><span class="ͼn">import</span><span> </span><span class="ͼt">QFont</span><br><span class="ͼn">from</span><span> </span><span class="ͼt">PySide6</span><span class="ͼn">.</span><span class="ͼt">QtWidgets</span><span> </span><span class="ͼn">import</span><span> (</span><br><span>    </span><span class="ͼt">QWidget</span><span>, </span><span class="ͼt">QVBoxLayout</span><span>, </span><span class="ͼt">QLabel</span><span>, </span><span class="ͼt">QTextEdit</span><span>, </span><span class="ͼt">QPushButton</span><span>,</span><br><span>    </span><span class="ͼt">QSizePolicy</span><span>, </span><span class="ͼt">QMessageBox</span><span>, </span><span class="ͼt">QScrollArea</span><br><span>)</span><br><br><span class="ͼn">import</span><span> </span><span class="ͼt">pandas</span><span> </span><span class="ͼn">as</span><span> </span><span class="ͼt">pd</span><br><span class="ͼn">import</span><span> </span><span class="ͼt">matplotlib</span><span class="ͼn">.</span><span class="ͼt">pyplot</span><span> </span><span class="ͼn">as</span><span> </span><span class="ͼt">plt</span><br><span class="ͼn">from</span><span> </span><span class="ͼt">matplotlib</span><span class="ͼn">.</span><span class="ͼt">backends</span><span class="ͼn">.</span><span class="ͼt">backend_qtagg</span><span> </span><span class="ͼn">import</span><span> </span><span class="ͼt">FigureCanvasQTAgg</span><span> </span><span class="ͼn">as</span><span> </span><span class="ͼt">FigureCanvas</span><br><br><br><span class="ͼn">class</span><span> </span><span class="ͼs">AIMetricsTab</span><span>(</span><span class="ͼt">QWidget</span><span>):</span><br><span>    </span><span class="ͼr">"""</span><br><span class="ͼr">    ===============================================================</span><br><span class="ͼr">    📊 AI Metrics Dashboard</span><br><span class="ͼr">    ---------------------------------------------------------------</span><br><span class="ͼr">    Displays training metrics, model statistics, and performance</span><br><span class="ͼr">    history for the AI trading system.</span><br><span class="ͼr">    ===============================================================</span><br><span class="ͼr">    """</span><br><br><span>    </span><span class="ͼn">def</span><span> </span><span class="ͼt">__init__</span><span>(</span><span class="ͼt">self</span><span>):</span><br><span>        </span><span class="ͼt">super</span><span>()</span><span class="ͼn">.</span><span>__init__()</span><br><br><span>        </span><span class="ͼt">self</span><span class="ͼn">.</span><span>metrics_path </span><span class="ͼn">=</span><span> </span><span class="ͼt">Path</span><span>(</span><span class="ͼr">"src/logs"</span><span>)</span><br><span>        </span><span class="ͼt">self</span><span class="ͼn">.</span><span>summary_path </span><span class="ͼn">=</span><span> </span><span class="ͼt">Path</span><span>(</span><span class="ͼr">"src/logs/metric_summary.log"</span><span>)</span><br><br><span>        </span><span class="ͼt">self</span><span class="ͼn">.</span><span>metrics_path</span><span class="ͼn">.</span><span>mkdir(</span><span class="ͼt">parents</span><span class="ͼn">=</span><span class="ͼq">True</span><span>, </span><span class="ͼt">exist_ok</span><span class="ͼn">=</span><span class="ͼq">True</span><span>)</span><br><br><span>        </span><span class="ͼt">main_layout</span><span> </span><span class="ͼn">=</span><span> </span><span class="ͼt">QVBoxLayout</span><span>(</span><span class="ͼt">self</span><span>)</span><br><br><span>        </span><span class="ͼl"># Scroll container</span><br><span>        </span><span class="ͼt">scroll</span><span> </span><span class="ͼn">=</span><span> </span><span class="ͼt">QScrollArea</span><span>()</span><br><span>        </span><span class="ͼt">scroll</span><span class="ͼn">.</span><span>setWidgetResizable(</span><span class="ͼq">True</span><span>)</span><br><br><span>        </span><span class="ͼt">content</span><span> </span><span class="ͼn">=</span><span> </span><span class="ͼt">QWidget</span><span>()</span><br><span>        </span><span class="ͼt">self</span><span class="ͼn">.</span><span>layout </span><span class="ͼn">=</span><span> </span><span class="ͼt">QVBoxLayout</span><span>(</span><span class="ͼt">content</span><span>)</span><br><br><span>        </span><span class="ͼt">scroll</span><span class="ͼn">.</span><span>setWidget(</span><span class="ͼt">content</span><span>)</span><br><span>        </span><span class="ͼt">main_layout</span><span class="ͼn">.</span><span>addWidget(</span><span class="ͼt">scroll</span><span>)</span><br><br><span>        </span><span class="ͼt">header</span><span> </span><span class="ͼn">=</span><span> </span><span class="ͼt">QLabel</span><span>(</span><span class="ͼr">"&lt;h2&gt;📊 AI Training Metrics&lt;/h2&gt;"</span><span>)</span><br><span>        </span><span class="ͼt">header</span><span class="ͼn">.</span><span>setAlignment(</span><span class="ͼt">Qt</span><span class="ͼn">.</span><span>AlignCenter)</span><br><br><span>        </span><span class="ͼt">self</span><span class="ͼn">.</span><span>layout</span><span class="ͼn">.</span><span>addWidget(</span><span class="ͼt">header</span><span>)</span><br><br><span>        </span><span class="ͼl"># =====================================================</span><br><span>        </span><span class="ͼl"># Training Summary</span><br><span>        </span><span class="ͼl"># =====================================================</span><br><br><span>        </span><span class="ͼt">self</span><span class="ͼn">.</span><span>summary_label </span><span class="ͼn">=</span><span> </span><span class="ͼt">QLabel</span><span>(</span><span class="ͼr">"📄 Training Summary"</span><span>)</span><br><span>        </span><span class="ͼt">self</span><span class="ͼn">.</span><span>summary_label</span><span class="ͼn">.</span><span>setFont(</span><span class="ͼt">QFont</span><span>(</span><span class="ͼr">"Segoe UI"</span><span>, </span><span class="ͼq">11</span><span>))</span><br><br><span>        </span><span class="ͼt">self</span><span class="ͼn">.</span><span>layout</span><span class="ͼn">.</span><span>addWidget(</span><span class="ͼt">self</span><span class="ͼn">.</span><span>summary_label)</span><br><br><span>        </span><span class="ͼt">self</span><span class="ͼn">.</span><span>summary_text </span><span class="ͼn">=</span><span> </span><span class="ͼt">QTextEdit</span><span>()</span><br><span>        </span><span class="ͼt">self</span><span class="ͼn">.</span><span>summary_text</span><span class="ͼn">.</span><span>setReadOnly(</span><span class="ͼq">True</span><span>)</span><br><span>        </span><span class="ͼt">self</span><span class="ͼn">.</span><span>summary_text</span><span class="ͼn">.</span><span>setFont(</span><span class="ͼt">QFont</span><span>(</span><span class="ͼr">"Consolas"</span><span>, </span><span class="ͼq">10</span><span>))</span><br><br><span>        </span><span class="ͼt">self</span><span class="ͼn">.</span><span>layout</span><span class="ͼn">.</span><span>addWidget(</span><span class="ͼt">self</span><span class="ͼn">.</span><span>summary_text)</span><br><br><span>        </span><span class="ͼl"># =====================================================</span><br><span>        </span><span class="ͼl"># Buttons</span><br><span>        </span><span class="ͼl"># =====================================================</span><br><br><span>        </span><span class="ͼt">self</span><span class="ͼn">.</span><span>reload_button </span><span class="ͼn">=</span><span> </span><span class="ͼt">QPushButton</span><span>(</span><span class="ͼr">"🔄 Reload Metrics"</span><span>)</span><br><span>        </span><span class="ͼt">self</span><span class="ͼn">.</span><span>reload_button</span><span class="ͼn">.</span><span>clicked</span><span class="ͼn">.</span><span>connect(</span><span class="ͼt">self</span><span class="ͼn">.</span><span>reload_metrics)</span><br><br><span>        </span><span class="ͼt">self</span><span class="ͼn">.</span><span>layout</span><span class="ͼn">.</span><span>addWidget(</span><span class="ͼt">self</span><span class="ͼn">.</span><span>reload_button)</span><br><br><span>        </span><span class="ͼt">self</span><span class="ͼn">.</span><span>chart_widget </span><span class="ͼn">=</span><span> </span><span class="ͼq">None</span><br><br><span>        </span><span class="ͼt">self</span><span class="ͼn">.</span><span>reload_metrics()</span><br><br><span>    </span><span class="ͼl"># ============================================================</span><br><span>    </span><span class="ͼl"># Reload metrics</span><br><span>    </span><span class="ͼl"># ============================================================</span><br><span>    </span><span class="ͼn">def</span><span> </span><span class="ͼt">reload_metrics</span><span>(</span><span class="ͼt">self</span><span>):</span><br><br><span>        </span><span class="ͼt">self</span><span class="ͼn">.</span><span>load_training_summary()</span><br><span>        </span><span class="ͼt">self</span><span class="ͼn">.</span><span>load_metric_charts()</span><br><br><span>    </span><span class="ͼl"># ============================================================</span><br><span>    </span><span class="ͼl"># Load summary</span><br><span>    </span><span class="ͼl"># ============================================================</span><br><span>    </span><span class="ͼn">def</span><span> </span><span class="ͼt">load_training_summary</span><span>(</span><span class="ͼt">self</span><span>):</span><br><br><span>        </span><span class="ͼn">try</span><span>:</span><br><br><span>            </span><span class="ͼn">if</span><span> </span><span class="ͼt">self</span><span class="ͼn">.</span><span>summary_path</span><span class="ͼn">.</span><span>exists():</span><br><br><span>                </span><span class="ͼt">txt</span><span> </span><span class="ͼn">=</span><span> </span><span class="ͼt">self</span><span class="ͼn">.</span><span>summary_path</span><span class="ͼn">.</span><span>read_text()</span><br><br><span>                </span><span class="ͼt">self</span><span class="ͼn">.</span><span>summary_text</span><span class="ͼn">.</span><span>setText(</span><span class="ͼt">txt</span><span>)</span><br><br><span>            </span><span class="ͼn">else</span><span>:</span><br><br><span>                </span><span class="ͼt">self</span><span class="ͼn">.</span><span>summary_text</span><span class="ͼn">.</span><span>setText(</span><br><span>                    </span><span class="ͼr">"⚠️ No training summary found.</span><span class="ͼx">\n</span><span class="ͼr">"</span><br><span>                    </span><span class="ͼr">"Run a training session first."</span><br><span>                )</span><br><br><span>        </span><span class="ͼn">except</span><span> </span><span class="ͼt">Exception</span><span> </span><span class="ͼn">as</span><span> </span><span class="ͼt">e</span><span>:</span><br><br><span>            </span><span class="ͼt">logging</span><span class="ͼn">.</span><span>error(</span><span class="ͼt">e</span><span>)</span><br><br><span>            </span><span class="ͼt">self</span><span class="ͼn">.</span><span>summary_text</span><span class="ͼn">.</span><span>setText(</span><span class="ͼr">f"Error loading summary:</span><span class="ͼx">\n</span><span>{</span><span class="ͼt">e</span><span>}</span><span class="ͼr">"</span><span>)</span><br><br><span>    </span><span class="ͼl"># ============================================================</span><br><span>    </span><span class="ͼl"># Load charts</span><br><span>    </span><span class="ͼl"># ============================================================</span><br><span>    </span><span class="ͼn">def</span><span> </span><span class="ͼt">load_metric_charts</span><span>(</span><span class="ͼt">self</span><span>):</span><br><br><span>        </span><span class="ͼt">self</span><span class="ͼn">.</span><span>_clear_chart()</span><br><br><span>        </span><span class="ͼn">try</span><span>:</span><br><br><span>            </span><span class="ͼt">files</span><span> </span><span class="ͼn">=</span><span> </span><span class="ͼt">list</span><span>(</span><span class="ͼt">self</span><span class="ͼn">.</span><span>metrics_path</span><span class="ͼn">.</span><span>glob(</span><span class="ͼr">"*training_metrics.csv"</span><span>))</span><br><br><span>            </span><span class="ͼn">if</span><span> </span><span class="ͼn">not</span><span> </span><span class="ͼt">files</span><span>:</span><br><span>                </span><span class="ͼn">return</span><span> </span><span class="ͼt">self</span><span class="ͼn">.</span><span>_show_message(</span><span class="ͼr">"ℹ️ No training metrics available."</span><span>)</span><br><br><span>            </span><span class="ͼt">latest</span><span> </span><span class="ͼn">=</span><span> </span><span class="ͼt">max</span><span>(</span><span class="ͼt">files</span><span>, </span><span class="ͼt">key</span><span class="ͼn">=</span><span class="ͼt">os</span><span class="ͼn">.</span><span>path</span><span class="ͼn">.</span><span>getmtime)</span><br><br><span>            </span><span class="ͼt">df</span><span> </span><span class="ͼn">=</span><span> </span><span class="ͼt">pd</span><span class="ͼn">.</span><span>read_csv(</span><span class="ͼt">latest</span><span>)</span><br><br><span>            </span><span class="ͼt">chart</span><span> </span><span class="ͼn">=</span><span> </span><span class="ͼt">self</span><span class="ͼn">.</span><span>_plot_metrics(</span><span class="ͼt">df</span><span>)</span><br><br><span>            </span><span class="ͼt">self</span><span class="ͼn">.</span><span>chart_widget </span><span class="ͼn">=</span><span> </span><span class="ͼt">chart</span><br><br><span>            </span><span class="ͼt">self</span><span class="ͼn">.</span><span>layout</span><span class="ͼn">.</span><span>addWidget(</span><span class="ͼt">chart</span><span>)</span><br><br><span>        </span><span class="ͼn">except</span><span> </span><span class="ͼt">Exception</span><span> </span><span class="ͼn">as</span><span> </span><span class="ͼt">e</span><span>:</span><br><br><span>            </span><span class="ͼt">logging</span><span class="ͼn">.</span><span>error(</span><span class="ͼt">e</span><span>)</span><br><br><span>            </span><span class="ͼt">self</span><span class="ͼn">.</span><span>_show_message(</span><span class="ͼr">f"❌ Failed to load metrics:</span><span class="ͼx">\n</span><span>{</span><span class="ͼt">e</span><span>}</span><span class="ͼr">"</span><span>)</span><br><br><span>    </span><span class="ͼl"># ============================================================</span><br><span>    </span><span class="ͼl"># Plot metrics</span><br><span>    </span><span class="ͼl"># ============================================================</span><br><span>    </span><span class="ͼn">def</span><span> </span><span class="ͼt">_plot_metrics</span><span>(</span><span class="ͼt">self</span><span>, </span><span class="ͼt">df</span><span>):</span><br><br><span>        </span><span class="ͼt">fig</span><span>, </span><span class="ͼt">ax</span><span> </span><span class="ͼn">=</span><span> </span><span class="ͼt">plt</span><span class="ͼn">.</span><span>subplots(</span><span class="ͼt">figsize</span><span class="ͼn">=</span><span>(</span><span class="ͼq">8</span><span>, </span><span class="ͼq">5</span><span>))</span><br><br><span>        </span><span class="ͼn">for</span><span> </span><span class="ͼt">col</span><span> </span><span class="ͼn">in</span><span> </span><span class="ͼt">df</span><span class="ͼn">.</span><span>columns:</span><br><br><span>            </span><span class="ͼn">if</span><span> </span><span class="ͼt">col</span><span class="ͼn">.</span><span>lower() </span><span class="ͼn">==</span><span> </span><span class="ͼr">"timestamp"</span><span>:</span><br><span>                </span><span class="ͼn">continue</span><br><br><span>            </span><span class="ͼt">ax</span><span class="ͼn">.</span><span>plot(</span><span class="ͼt">df</span><span>[</span><span class="ͼt">col</span><span>], </span><span class="ͼt">label</span><span class="ͼn">=</span><span class="ͼt">col</span><span>)</span><br><br><span>        </span><span class="ͼt">ax</span><span class="ͼn">.</span><span>set_title(</span><span class="ͼr">"AI Training Metrics"</span><span>)</span><br><span>        </span><span class="ͼt">ax</span><span class="ͼn">.</span><span>set_xlabel(</span><span class="ͼr">"Training Run"</span><span>)</span><br><span>        </span><span class="ͼt">ax</span><span class="ͼn">.</span><span>set_ylabel(</span><span class="ͼr">"Metric Value"</span><span>)</span><br><br><span>        </span><span class="ͼt">ax</span><span class="ͼn">.</span><span>legend()</span><br><span>        </span><span class="ͼt">ax</span><span class="ͼn">.</span><span>grid(</span><span class="ͼq">True</span><span>)</span><br><br><span>        </span><span class="ͼt">canvas</span><span> </span><span class="ͼn">=</span><span> </span><span class="ͼt">FigureCanvas</span><span>(</span><span class="ͼt">fig</span><span>)</span><br><br><span>        </span><span class="ͼt">canvas</span><span class="ͼn">.</span><span>setSizePolicy(</span><span class="ͼt">QSizePolicy</span><span class="ͼn">.</span><span>Expanding, </span><span class="ͼt">QSizePolicy</span><span class="ͼn">.</span><span>Expanding)</span><br><br><span>        </span><span class="ͼn">return</span><span> </span><span class="ͼt">canvas</span><br><br><span>    </span><span class="ͼl"># ============================================================</span><br><span>    </span><span class="ͼl"># Message</span><br><span>    </span><span class="ͼl"># ============================================================</span><br><span>    </span><span class="ͼn">def</span><span> </span><span class="ͼt">_show_message</span><span>(</span><span class="ͼt">self</span><span>, </span><span class="ͼt">msg</span><span>):</span><br><br><span>        </span><span class="ͼt">box</span><span> </span><span class="ͼn">=</span><span> </span><span class="ͼt">QTextEdit</span><span>()</span><br><br><span>        </span><span class="ͼt">box</span><span class="ͼn">.</span><span>setText(</span><span class="ͼt">msg</span><span>)</span><br><br><span>        </span><span class="ͼt">box</span><span class="ͼn">.</span><span>setReadOnly(</span><span class="ͼq">True</span><span>)</span><br><br><span>        </span><span class="ͼt">self</span><span class="ͼn">.</span><span>layout</span><span class="ͼn">.</span><span>addWidget(</span><span class="ͼt">box</span><span>)</span><br><br><span>    </span><span class="ͼl"># ============================================================</span><br><span>    </span><span class="ͼl"># Clear chart</span><br><span>    </span><span class="ͼl"># ============================================================</span><br><span>    </span><span class="ͼn">def</span><span> </span><span class="ͼt">_clear_chart</span><span>(</span><span class="ͼt">self</span><span>):</span><br><br><span>        </span><span class="ͼn">if</span><span> </span><span class="ͼt">self</span><span class="ͼn">.</span><span>chart_widget:</span><br><br><span>            </span><span class="ͼt">self</span><span class="ͼn">.</span><span>layout</span><span class="ͼn">.</span><span>removeWidget(</span><span class="ͼt">self</span><span class="ͼn">.</span><span>chart_widget)</span><br><br><span>            </span><span class="ͼt">self</span><span class="ͼn">.</span><span>chart_widget</span><span class="ͼn">.</span><span>deleteLater()</span><br><br><span>            </span><span class="ͼt">self</span><span class="ͼn">.</span><span>chart_widget </span><span class="ͼn">=</span><span> </span><span class="ͼq">None</span></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=""><div class="" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"></div></div></div></div></div></pre>
