<p data-start="795" data-end="808">Replace with:</p>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="810" data-end="1058"><div class="relative w-full mt-4 mb-1"><div class=""><div class="relative"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"><div class="border border-token-border-light border-radius-3xl corner-superellipse/1.1 rounded-3xl"><div class="h-full w-full border-radius-3xl bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary corner-superellipse/1.1 overflow-clip rounded-3xl lxnfua_clipPathFallback"><div class="sticky z-2 select-none top-(--sticky-padding-top)"><div class="flex w-full items-center justify-between py-1.5 ps-4 pe-1.5 font-sans md:ps-5 bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary"><div class="flex max-w-[75%] min-w-0 cursor-default items-center text-sm font-medium justify-self-start text-token-text-primary"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-sm me-2.5 shrink-0"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-ni7q5mnh.svg#e45ab3" fill="currentColor"></use></svg>Python</div><div class="flex flex-row items-center gap-0.5 justify-self-end"><button class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none py-2 text-sm font-medium hover:bg-black/5 dark:hover:bg-white/10 size-9 rounded-full px-2" aria-label="Copy" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-md"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-ni7q5mnh.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button><button class="btn relative group-focus-within/dialog:focus-visible:[outline-width:1.5px] group-focus-within/dialog:focus-visible:[outline-offset:2.5px] group-focus-within/dialog:focus-visible:[outline-style:solid] group-focus-within/dialog:focus-visible:[outline-color:var(--text-primary)] btn-ghost border-token-border-default ms-2 border font-sans" aria-label="Run code" type="button"><div class="flex w-full items-center justify-center gap-1.5"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-label="" class="-ms-0.5 icon"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-ni7q5mnh.svg#6ef7a4" fill="currentColor"></use></svg>Run</div></button></div></div></div><div class="pointer-events-none absolute inset-x-4 top-12 bottom-4"><div class="pointer-events-none sticky z-40 shrink-0 z-1!" style="top: calc(calc(var(--sticky-padding-top) + 48px) - 1px * 3); margin-bottom: calc(-4px); height: calc(4px); mask-image: linear-gradient(transparent 25%, white 75%);"><div class="sticky bg-token-border-light" style="top: calc(var(--sticky-padding-top) + 48px); height: 1px;"></div></div></div><div class="" style="transform: none;"><div class="relative z-0 flex max-w-full"><div id="code-block-viewer" dir="ltr" class="q9tKkq_viewer cm-editor z-10 light:cm-light dark:cm-light flex h-full w-full flex-col items-stretch ͼk ͼy"><div class="cm-scroller"><div class="cm-content q9tKkq_readonly"><span class="ͼt">exchange_class</span><span> </span><span class="ͼn">=</span><span> </span><span class="ͼt">getattr</span><span>(</span><span class="ͼt">ccxt</span><span>, </span><span class="ͼt">self</span><span class="ͼn">.</span><span>exchange_name)</span><br><br><span class="ͼt">self</span><span class="ͼn">.</span><span>exchange </span><span class="ͼn">=</span><span> </span><span class="ͼt">exchange_class</span><span>({</span><br><span>    </span><span class="ͼr">"apiKey"</span><span>: </span><span class="ͼt">self</span><span class="ͼn">.</span><span>api_key,</span><br><span>    </span><span class="ͼr">"secret"</span><span>: </span><span class="ͼt">self</span><span class="ͼn">.</span><span>secret,</span><br><span>    </span><span class="ͼr">"enableRateLimit"</span><span>: </span><span class="ͼq">True</span><span>,</span><br><span>    </span><span class="ͼr">"options"</span><span>: {</span><br><span>        </span><span class="ͼr">"adjustForTimeDifference"</span><span>: </span><span class="ͼq">True</span><br><span>    }</span><br><span>})</span></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=""><div class="" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"></div></div></div></div></div></pre>
<p data-start="1060" data-end="1118">This tells CCXT to <strong data-start="1079" data-end="1117">auto-sync with Binance server time</strong>.</p>
<hr data-start="1120" data-end="1123">
<h1 data-section-id="1qzugni" data-start="1125" data-end="1177">✅ Solution 2 — Manually Sync Time (Good extra fix)</h1>
<p data-start="1179" data-end="1190">On Windows:</p>
<p data-start="1192" data-end="1245">1️⃣ Open <strong data-start="1201" data-end="1245">Settings → Time &amp; Language → Date &amp; Time</strong></p>
<p data-start="1247" data-end="1259">2️⃣ Turn ON:</p>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="1261" data-end="1291"><div class="relative w-full mt-4 mb-1"><div class=""><div class="relative"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"><div class="border border-token-border-light border-radius-3xl corner-superellipse/1.1 rounded-3xl"><div class="h-full w-full border-radius-3xl bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary corner-superellipse/1.1 overflow-clip rounded-3xl lxnfua_clipPathFallback"><div class="pointer-events-none absolute end-1.5 top-1 z-2 md:end-2 md:top-1"><button class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none pointer-events-auto py-2 text-sm font-medium hover:bg-black/5 dark:hover:bg-white/10 size-9 rounded-full px-2" aria-label="Copy" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-md"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-ni7q5mnh.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button></div><div class="pt-3" style="transform: none;"><div class="relative z-0 flex max-w-full"><div id="code-block-viewer" dir="ltr" class="q9tKkq_viewer cm-editor z-10 light:cm-light dark:cm-light flex h-full w-full flex-col items-stretch ͼk ͼy"><div class="cm-scroller"><div class="cm-content q9tKkq_readonly"><span>Set time automatically</span></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=""><div class="" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"></div></div></div></div></div></pre>
<p data-start="1293" data-end="1303">3️⃣ Click:</p>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="1305" data-end="1321"><div class="relative w-full mt-4 mb-1"><div class=""><div class="relative"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"><div class="border border-token-border-light border-radius-3xl corner-superellipse/1.1 rounded-3xl"><div class="h-full w-full border-radius-3xl bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary corner-superellipse/1.1 overflow-clip rounded-3xl lxnfua_clipPathFallback"><div class="pointer-events-none absolute end-1.5 top-1 z-2 md:end-2 md:top-1"><button class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none pointer-events-auto py-2 text-sm font-medium hover:bg-black/5 dark:hover:bg-white/10 size-9 rounded-full px-2" aria-label="Copy" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-md"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-ni7q5mnh.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button></div><div class="pt-3" style="transform: none;"><div class="relative z-0 flex max-w-full"><div id="code-block-viewer" dir="ltr" class="q9tKkq_viewer cm-editor z-10 light:cm-light dark:cm-light flex h-full w-full flex-col items-stretch ͼk ͼy"><div class="cm-scroller"><div class="cm-content q9tKkq_readonly"><span>Sync now</span></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=""><div class="" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"></div></div></div></div></div></pre>
<hr data-start="1323" data-end="1326">
<h1 data-section-id="16qcjcu" data-start="1328" data-end="1368">✅ Solution 3 — Increase receive window</h1>
<p data-start="1370" data-end="1415">Binance allows a <strong data-start="1387" data-end="1414">larger tolerance window</strong>.</p>
<p data-start="1417" data-end="1421">Add:</p>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="1423" data-end="1456"><div class="relative w-full mt-4 mb-1"><div class=""><div class="relative"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"><div class="border border-token-border-light border-radius-3xl corner-superellipse/1.1 rounded-3xl"><div class="h-full w-full border-radius-3xl bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary corner-superellipse/1.1 overflow-clip rounded-3xl lxnfua_clipPathFallback"><div class="sticky z-2 select-none top-(--sticky-padding-top)"><div class="flex w-full items-center justify-between py-1.5 ps-4 pe-1.5 font-sans md:ps-5 bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary"><div class="flex max-w-[75%] min-w-0 cursor-default items-center text-sm font-medium justify-self-start text-token-text-primary"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-sm me-2.5 shrink-0"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-ni7q5mnh.svg#e45ab3" fill="currentColor"></use></svg>Python</div><div class="flex flex-row items-center gap-0.5 justify-self-end"><button class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none py-2 text-sm font-medium hover:bg-black/5 dark:hover:bg-white/10 size-9 rounded-full px-2" aria-label="Copy" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-md"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-ni7q5mnh.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button><button class="btn relative group-focus-within/dialog:focus-visible:[outline-width:1.5px] group-focus-within/dialog:focus-visible:[outline-offset:2.5px] group-focus-within/dialog:focus-visible:[outline-style:solid] group-focus-within/dialog:focus-visible:[outline-color:var(--text-primary)] btn-ghost border-token-border-default ms-2 border font-sans" aria-label="Run code" type="button"><div class="flex w-full items-center justify-center gap-1.5"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-label="" class="-ms-0.5 icon"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-ni7q5mnh.svg#6ef7a4" fill="currentColor"></use></svg>Run</div></button></div></div></div><div class="pointer-events-none absolute inset-x-4 top-12 bottom-4"><div class="pointer-events-none sticky z-40 shrink-0 z-1!" style="top: calc(calc(var(--sticky-padding-top) + 48px) - 1px * 3); margin-bottom: calc(-4px); height: calc(4px); mask-image: linear-gradient(transparent 25%, white 75%);"><div class="sticky bg-token-border-light" style="top: calc(var(--sticky-padding-top) + 48px); height: 1px;"></div></div></div><div class="" style="transform: none;"><div class="relative z-0 flex max-w-full"><div id="code-block-viewer" dir="ltr" class="q9tKkq_viewer cm-editor z-10 light:cm-light dark:cm-light flex h-full w-full flex-col items-stretch ͼk ͼy"><div class="cm-scroller"><div class="cm-content q9tKkq_readonly"><span class="ͼr">"recvWindow"</span><span>: </span><span class="ͼq">10000</span></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=""><div class="" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"></div></div></div></div></div></pre>
<p data-start="1458" data-end="1466">Example:</p>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="1468" data-end="1689"><div class="relative w-full mt-4 mb-1"><div class=""><div class="relative"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"><div class="border border-token-border-light border-radius-3xl corner-superellipse/1.1 rounded-3xl"><div class="h-full w-full border-radius-3xl bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary corner-superellipse/1.1 overflow-clip rounded-3xl lxnfua_clipPathFallback"><div class="sticky z-2 select-none top-(--sticky-padding-top)"><div class="flex w-full items-center justify-between py-1.5 ps-4 pe-1.5 font-sans md:ps-5 bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary"><div class="flex max-w-[75%] min-w-0 cursor-default items-center text-sm font-medium justify-self-start text-token-text-primary"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-sm me-2.5 shrink-0"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-ni7q5mnh.svg#e45ab3" fill="currentColor"></use></svg>Python</div><div class="flex flex-row items-center gap-0.5 justify-self-end"><button class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none py-2 text-sm font-medium hover:bg-black/5 dark:hover:bg-white/10 size-9 rounded-full px-2" aria-label="Copy" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-md"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-ni7q5mnh.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button><button class="btn relative group-focus-within/dialog:focus-visible:[outline-width:1.5px] group-focus-within/dialog:focus-visible:[outline-offset:2.5px] group-focus-within/dialog:focus-visible:[outline-style:solid] group-focus-within/dialog:focus-visible:[outline-color:var(--text-primary)] btn-ghost border-token-border-default ms-2 border font-sans" aria-label="Run code" type="button"><div class="flex w-full items-center justify-center gap-1.5"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-label="" class="-ms-0.5 icon"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-ni7q5mnh.svg#6ef7a4" fill="currentColor"></use></svg>Run</div></button></div></div></div><div class="pointer-events-none absolute inset-x-4 top-12 bottom-4"><div class="pointer-events-none sticky z-40 shrink-0 z-1!" style="top: calc(calc(var(--sticky-padding-top) + 48px) - 1px * 3); margin-bottom: calc(-4px); height: calc(4px); mask-image: linear-gradient(transparent 25%, white 75%);"><div class="sticky bg-token-border-light" style="top: calc(var(--sticky-padding-top) + 48px); height: 1px;"></div></div></div><div class="" style="transform: none;"><div class="relative z-0 flex max-w-full"><div id="code-block-viewer" dir="ltr" class="q9tKkq_viewer cm-editor z-10 light:cm-light dark:cm-light flex h-full w-full flex-col items-stretch ͼk ͼy"><div class="cm-scroller"><div class="cm-content q9tKkq_readonly"><span class="ͼt">self</span><span class="ͼn">.</span><span>exchange </span><span class="ͼn">=</span><span> </span><span class="ͼt">exchange_class</span><span>({</span><br><span>    </span><span class="ͼr">"apiKey"</span><span>: </span><span class="ͼt">self</span><span class="ͼn">.</span><span>api_key,</span><br><span>    </span><span class="ͼr">"secret"</span><span>: </span><span class="ͼt">self</span><span class="ͼn">.</span><span>secret,</span><br><span>    </span><span class="ͼr">"enableRateLimit"</span><span>: </span><span class="ͼq">True</span><span>,</span><br><span>    </span><span class="ͼr">"options"</span><span>: {</span><br><span>        </span><span class="ͼr">"adjustForTimeDifference"</span><span>: </span><span class="ͼq">True</span><br><span>    },</span><br><span>    </span><span class="ͼr">"recvWindow"</span><span>: </span><span class="ͼq">10000</span><br><span>})</span></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=""><div class="" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"></div></div></div></div></div></pre>
<hr data-start="1691" data-end="1694">
<h1 data-section-id="2hdjhh" data-start="1696" data-end="1729">⭐ Best Production Configuration</h1>
<p data-start="1731" data-end="1780">Your broker initialization should look like this:</p>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="1782" data-end="2112"><div class="relative w-full mt-4 mb-1"><div class=""><div class="relative"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"><div class="border border-token-border-light border-radius-3xl corner-superellipse/1.1 rounded-3xl"><div class="h-full w-full border-radius-3xl bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary corner-superellipse/1.1 overflow-clip rounded-3xl lxnfua_clipPathFallback"><div class="sticky z-2 select-none top-(--sticky-padding-top)"><div class="flex w-full items-center justify-between py-1.5 ps-4 pe-1.5 font-sans md:ps-5 bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary"><div class="flex max-w-[75%] min-w-0 cursor-default items-center text-sm font-medium justify-self-start text-token-text-primary"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-sm me-2.5 shrink-0"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-ni7q5mnh.svg#e45ab3" fill="currentColor"></use></svg>Python</div><div class="flex flex-row items-center gap-0.5 justify-self-end"><button class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none py-2 text-sm font-medium hover:bg-black/5 dark:hover:bg-white/10 size-9 rounded-full px-2" aria-label="Copy" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-md"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-ni7q5mnh.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button><button class="btn relative group-focus-within/dialog:focus-visible:[outline-width:1.5px] group-focus-within/dialog:focus-visible:[outline-offset:2.5px] group-focus-within/dialog:focus-visible:[outline-style:solid] group-focus-within/dialog:focus-visible:[outline-color:var(--text-primary)] btn-ghost border-token-border-default ms-2 border font-sans" aria-label="Run code" type="button"><div class="flex w-full items-center justify-center gap-1.5"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-label="" class="-ms-0.5 icon"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-ni7q5mnh.svg#6ef7a4" fill="currentColor"></use></svg>Run</div></button></div></div></div><div class="pointer-events-none absolute inset-x-4 top-12 bottom-4"><div class="pointer-events-none sticky z-40 shrink-0 z-1!" style="top: calc(calc(var(--sticky-padding-top) + 48px) - 1px * 3); margin-bottom: calc(-4px); height: calc(4px); mask-image: linear-gradient(transparent 25%, white 75%);"><div class="sticky bg-token-border-light" style="top: calc(var(--sticky-padding-top) + 48px); height: 1px;"></div></div></div><div class="" style="transform: none;"><div class="relative z-0 flex max-w-full"><div id="code-block-viewer" dir="ltr" class="q9tKkq_viewer cm-editor z-10 light:cm-light dark:cm-light flex h-full w-full flex-col items-stretch ͼk ͼy"><div class="cm-scroller"><div class="cm-content q9tKkq_readonly"><span class="ͼn">import</span><span> </span><span class="ͼt">ccxt</span><span class="ͼn">.</span><span class="ͼt">async_support</span><span> </span><span class="ͼn">as</span><span> </span><span class="ͼt">ccxt</span><br><br><span class="ͼt">exchange_class</span><span> </span><span class="ͼn">=</span><span> </span><span class="ͼt">getattr</span><span>(</span><span class="ͼt">ccxt</span><span>, </span><span class="ͼt">self</span><span class="ͼn">.</span><span>exchange_name)</span><br><br><span class="ͼt">self</span><span class="ͼn">.</span><span>exchange </span><span class="ͼn">=</span><span> </span><span class="ͼt">exchange_class</span><span>({</span><br><span>    </span><span class="ͼr">"apiKey"</span><span>: </span><span class="ͼt">self</span><span class="ͼn">.</span><span>api_key,</span><br><span>    </span><span class="ͼr">"secret"</span><span>: </span><span class="ͼt">self</span><span class="ͼn">.</span><span>secret,</span><br><span>    </span><span class="ͼr">"enableRateLimit"</span><span>: </span><span class="ͼq">True</span><span>,</span><br><span>    </span><span class="ͼr">"timeout"</span><span>: </span><span class="ͼq">30000</span><span>,</span><br><span>    </span><span class="ͼr">"recvWindow"</span><span>: </span><span class="ͼq">10000</span><span>,</span><br><span>    </span><span class="ͼr">"options"</span><span>: {</span><br><span>        </span><span class="ͼr">"adjustForTimeDifference"</span><span>: </span><span class="ͼq">True</span><br><span>    }</span><br><span>})</span></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=""><div class="" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"></div></div></div></div></div></pre>
<p data-start="2114" data-end="2178">This configuration is <strong data-start="2136" data-end="2177">stable for production trading systems</strong>.</p>
<hr data-start="2180" data-end="2183">
<h1 data-section-id="jdopt4" data-start="2185" data-end="2212">⚠️ Another Issue I Notice</h1>
<p data-start="2214" data-end="2230">You are running:</p>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="2232" data-end="2251"><div class="relative w-full mt-4 mb-1"><div class=""><div class="relative"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"><div class="border border-token-border-light border-radius-3xl corner-superellipse/1.1 rounded-3xl"><div class="h-full w-full border-radius-3xl bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary corner-superellipse/1.1 overflow-clip rounded-3xl lxnfua_clipPathFallback"><div class="pointer-events-none absolute end-1.5 top-1 z-2 md:end-2 md:top-1"><button class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none pointer-events-auto py-2 text-sm font-medium hover:bg-black/5 dark:hover:bg-white/10 size-9 rounded-full px-2" aria-label="Copy" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-md"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-ni7q5mnh.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button></div><div class="pt-3" style="transform: none;"><div class="relative z-0 flex max-w-full"><div id="code-block-viewer" dir="ltr" class="q9tKkq_viewer cm-editor z-10 light:cm-light dark:cm-light flex h-full w-full flex-col items-stretch ͼk ͼy"><div class="cm-scroller"><div class="cm-content q9tKkq_readonly"><span>Python 3.14</span></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=""><div class="" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"></div></div></div></div></div></pre>
<p data-start="2253" data-end="2318">CCXT supports it, but <strong data-start="2275" data-end="2317">many AI / finance libraries do not yet</strong>.</p>
<p data-start="2320" data-end="2365">For trading systems the most stable stack is:</p>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="2367" data-end="2419"><div class="relative w-full mt-4 mb-1"><div class=""><div class="relative"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"><div class="border border-token-border-light border-radius-3xl corner-superellipse/1.1 rounded-3xl"><div class="h-full w-full border-radius-3xl bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary corner-superellipse/1.1 overflow-clip rounded-3xl lxnfua_clipPathFallback"><div class="pointer-events-none absolute end-1.5 top-1 z-2 md:end-2 md:top-1"><button class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none pointer-events-auto py-2 text-sm font-medium hover:bg-black/5 dark:hover:bg-white/10 size-9 rounded-full px-2" aria-label="Copy" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-md"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-ni7q5mnh.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button></div><div class="pt-3" style="transform: none;"><div class="relative z-0 flex max-w-full"><div id="code-block-viewer" dir="ltr" class="q9tKkq_viewer cm-editor z-10 light:cm-light dark:cm-light flex h-full w-full flex-col items-stretch ͼk ͼy"><div class="cm-scroller"><div class="cm-content q9tKkq_readonly"><span>Python 3.11</span><br><span>ccxt latest</span><br><span>numpy</span><br><span>pandas</span><br><span>xgboost</span></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=""><div class="" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"></div></div></div></div></div></pre>
<hr data-start="2421" data-end="2424">
<h1 data-section-id="1fwq5vj" data-start="2426" data-end="2464">🚀 Bonus Improvement for Your Broker</h1>
<p data-start="2466" data-end="2521">You should also add <strong data-start="2486" data-end="2520">automatic reconnect protection</strong>.</p>
<p data-start="2523" data-end="2531">Example:</p>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="2533" data-end="2873"><div class="relative w-full mt-4 mb-1"><div class=""><div class="relative"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"><div class="border border-token-border-light border-radius-3xl corner-superellipse/1.1 rounded-3xl"><div class="h-full w-full border-radius-3xl bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary corner-superellipse/1.1 overflow-clip rounded-3xl lxnfua_clipPathFallback"><div class="sticky z-2 select-none top-(--sticky-padding-top)"><div class="flex w-full items-center justify-between py-1.5 ps-4 pe-1.5 font-sans md:ps-5 bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary"><div class="flex max-w-[75%] min-w-0 cursor-default items-center text-sm font-medium justify-self-start text-token-text-primary"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-sm me-2.5 shrink-0"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-ni7q5mnh.svg#e45ab3" fill="currentColor"></use></svg>Python</div><div class="flex flex-row items-center gap-0.5 justify-self-end"><button class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none py-2 text-sm font-medium hover:bg-black/5 dark:hover:bg-white/10 size-9 rounded-full px-2" aria-label="Copy" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-md"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-ni7q5mnh.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button><button class="btn relative group-focus-within/dialog:focus-visible:[outline-width:1.5px] group-focus-within/dialog:focus-visible:[outline-offset:2.5px] group-focus-within/dialog:focus-visible:[outline-style:solid] group-focus-within/dialog:focus-visible:[outline-color:var(--text-primary)] btn-ghost border-token-border-default ms-2 border font-sans" aria-label="Run code" type="button"><div class="flex w-full items-center justify-center gap-1.5"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-label="" class="-ms-0.5 icon"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-ni7q5mnh.svg#6ef7a4" fill="currentColor"></use></svg>Run</div></button></div></div></div><div class="pointer-events-none absolute inset-x-4 top-12 bottom-4"><div class="pointer-events-none sticky z-40 shrink-0 z-1!" style="top: calc(calc(var(--sticky-padding-top) + 48px) - 1px * 3); margin-bottom: calc(-4px); height: calc(4px); mask-image: linear-gradient(transparent 25%, white 75%);"><div class="sticky bg-token-border-light" style="top: calc(var(--sticky-padding-top) + 48px); height: 1px;"></div></div></div><div class="" style="transform: none;"><div class="relative z-0 flex max-w-full"><div id="code-block-viewer" dir="ltr" class="q9tKkq_viewer cm-editor z-10 light:cm-light dark:cm-light flex h-full w-full flex-col items-stretch ͼk ͼy"><div class="cm-scroller"><div class="cm-content q9tKkq_readonly"><span class="ͼn">async</span><span> </span><span class="ͼn">def</span><span> </span><span class="ͼt">safe_load_markets</span><span>(</span><span class="ͼt">self</span><span>):</span><br><br><span>    </span><span class="ͼn">for</span><span> </span><span class="ͼt">_</span><span> </span><span class="ͼn">in</span><span> </span><span class="ͼt">range</span><span>(</span><span class="ͼq">3</span><span>):</span><br><span>        </span><span class="ͼn">try</span><span>:</span><br><span>            </span><span class="ͼn">await</span><span> </span><span class="ͼt">self</span><span class="ͼn">.</span><span>exchange</span><span class="ͼn">.</span><span>load_markets()</span><br><span>            </span><span class="ͼn">return</span><br><span>        </span><span class="ͼn">except</span><span> </span><span class="ͼt">Exception</span><span> </span><span class="ͼn">as</span><span> </span><span class="ͼt">e</span><span>:</span><br><span>            </span><span class="ͼt">self</span><span class="ͼn">.</span><span>logger</span><span class="ͼn">.</span><span>warning(</span><span class="ͼr">f"Market load retry: </span><span>{</span><span class="ͼt">e</span><span>}</span><span class="ͼr">"</span><span>)</span><br><span>            </span><span class="ͼn">await</span><span> </span><span class="ͼt">asyncio</span><span class="ͼn">.</span><span>sleep(</span><span class="ͼq">2</span><span>)</span><br><br><span>    </span><span class="ͼn">raise</span><span> </span><span class="ͼt">RuntimeError</span><span>(</span><span class="ͼr">"Failed to load markets after retries"</span><span>)</span></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=""><div class="" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"></div></div></div></div></div></pre>
<p data-start="2875" data-end="2918">This prevents crashes when Binance is slow.</p>
