<hr data-start="2923" data-end="2926">
<h1 data-section-id="1xcuqle" data-start="2928" data-end="2969">⭐ Next improvement I strongly recommend</h1>
<p data-start="2971" data-end="3037">Once this connection issue is solved, the <strong data-start="3013" data-end="3033">next big upgrade</strong> is:</p>
<h3 data-section-id="1c8yy8e" data-start="3039" data-end="3088">Replace REST polling with WebSocket streaming</h3>
<p data-start="3090" data-end="3094">Why:</p>
<div class="TyagGW_tableContainer"><div tabindex="-1" class="group TyagGW_tableWrapper flex flex-col-reverse w-fit"><table data-start="3096" data-end="3199" class="w-fit min-w-(--thread-content-width)"><thead data-start="3096" data-end="3116"><tr data-start="3096" data-end="3116"><th data-start="3096" data-end="3103" data-col-size="sm" class="">REST</th><th data-start="3103" data-end="3116" data-col-size="sm" class="">WebSocket</th></tr></thead><tbody data-start="3131" data-end="3199"><tr data-start="3131" data-end="3151"><td data-start="3131" data-end="3138" data-col-size="sm">slow</td><td data-start="3138" data-end="3151" data-col-size="sm">real-time</td></tr><tr data-start="3152" data-end="3179"><td data-start="3152" data-end="3166" data-col-size="sm">rate limits</td><td data-start="3166" data-end="3179" data-col-size="sm">unlimited</td></tr><tr data-start="3180" data-end="3199"><td data-start="3180" data-end="3190" data-col-size="sm">latency</td><td data-start="3190" data-end="3199" data-col-size="sm">&lt;10ms</td></tr></tbody></table><div class="sticky h-0 select-none end-(--thread-content-margin) self-end"><div class="absolute end-0 flex items-end" style="height: 32.7969px;"><span class="" data-state="closed"><button aria-label="Copy table" class="hover:bg-token-bg-tertiary text-token-text-secondary my-1 rounded-sm p-1 transition-opacity group-[:not(:hover):not(:focus-within)]:pointer-events-none group-[:not(:hover):not(:focus-within)]:opacity-0"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-ni7q5mnh.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button></span></div></div></div></div>
<p data-start="3201" data-end="3269">This would make your <strong data-start="3222" data-end="3268">Sopotek trading engine institutional-level</strong>.</p>
<hr data-start="3271" data-end="3274">
<p data-start="3276" data-end="3358">If you want, I can also show you <strong data-start="3309" data-end="3347">a very powerful CCXTBroker upgrade</strong> that will:</p>
<ul data-start="3360" data-end="3472" data-is-last-node="" data-is-only-node="">
<li data-section-id="udr8y3" data-start="3360" data-end="3386">
<p data-start="3362" data-end="3386">stream <strong data-start="3369" data-end="3386">1000+ symbols</strong></p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1oquyf7" data-start="3387" data-end="3403">
<p data-start="3389" data-end="3403">auto-reconnect</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="r5j2lr" data-start="3404" data-end="3422">
<p data-start="3406" data-end="3422">auto-resync time</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="qlly2t" data-start="3423" data-end="3472" data-is-last-node="">
<p data-start="3425" data-end="3472" data-is-last-node="">feed candles directly to your <strong data-start="3455" data-end="3471">CandleBuffer</strong>.</p>
