<ol data-start="64" data-end="326">
<li data-section-id="bkjk20" data-start="64" data-end="136">
<p data-start="67" data-end="136">You created an <strong data-start="82" data-end="101">aiohttp session</strong> but you <strong data-start="110" data-end="135">never pass it to CCXT</strong>.</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="151bt12" data-start="137" data-end="211">
<p data-start="140" data-end="211">You <strong data-start="144" data-end="172">didn't sync Binance time</strong> (needed for the <code data-start="189" data-end="203">InvalidNonce</code> error).</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="fs5zhy" data-start="212" data-end="248">
<p data-start="215" data-end="248">There is <strong data-start="224" data-end="247">no reconnect safety</strong>.</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="9o9uvb" data-start="249" data-end="287">
<p data-start="252" data-end="287">There is <strong data-start="261" data-end="286">no cleanup protection</strong>.</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1n01vle" data-start="288" data-end="326">
<p data-start="291" data-end="326">There is <strong data-start="300" data-end="325">no <code data-start="305" data-end="317">_connected</code> state</strong>.</p>
