<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="1740" data-end="1807"><div class="relative w-full mt-4 mb-1"><div class=""><div class="relative"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"><div class="border border-token-border-light border-radius-3xl corner-superellipse/1.1 rounded-3xl"><div class="h-full w-full border-radius-3xl bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary corner-superellipse/1.1 overflow-clip rounded-3xl lxnfua_clipPathFallback"><div class="sticky z-2 select-none top-(--sticky-padding-top)"><div class="flex w-full items-center justify-between py-1.5 ps-4 pe-1.5 font-sans md:ps-5 bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary"><div class="flex max-w-[75%] min-w-0 cursor-default items-center text-sm font-medium justify-self-start text-token-text-primary"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-sm me-2.5 shrink-0"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-ni7q5mnh.svg#e45ab3" fill="currentColor"></use></svg>Python</div><div class="flex flex-row items-center gap-0.5 justify-self-end"><button class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none py-2 text-sm font-medium hover:bg-black/5 dark:hover:bg-white/10 size-9 rounded-full px-2" aria-label="Copy" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-md"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-ni7q5mnh.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button><button class="btn relative group-focus-within/dialog:focus-visible:[outline-width:1.5px] group-focus-within/dialog:focus-visible:[outline-offset:2.5px] group-focus-within/dialog:focus-visible:[outline-style:solid] group-focus-within/dialog:focus-visible:[outline-color:var(--text-primary)] btn-ghost border-token-border-default ms-2 border font-sans" aria-label="Run code" type="button"><div class="flex w-full items-center justify-center gap-1.5"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-label="" class="-ms-0.5 icon"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-ni7q5mnh.svg#6ef7a4" fill="currentColor"></use></svg>Run</div></button></div></div></div><div class="pointer-events-none absolute inset-x-4 top-12 bottom-4"><div class="pointer-events-none sticky z-40 shrink-0 z-1!" style="top: calc(calc(var(--sticky-padding-top) + 48px) - 1px * 3); margin-bottom: calc(-4px); height: calc(4px); mask-image: linear-gradient(transparent 25%, white 75%);"><div class="sticky bg-token-border-light" style="top: calc(var(--sticky-padding-top) + 48px); height: 1px;"></div></div></div><div class="" style="transform: none;"><div class="relative z-0 flex max-w-full"><div id="code-block-viewer" dir="ltr" class="q9tKkq_viewer cm-editor z-10 light:cm-light dark:cm-light flex h-full w-full flex-col items-stretch ͼk ͼy"><div class="cm-scroller"><div class="cm-content q9tKkq_readonly"><span class="ͼt">loop</span><span class="ͼn">.</span><span>create_task(</span><span class="ͼt">self</span><span class="ͼn">.</span><span>controller</span><span class="ͼn">.</span><span>trading_app</span><span class="ͼn">.</span><span>start())</span></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=""><div class="" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"></div></div></div></div></div></pre>
<p data-start="1809" data-end="1837">But <code data-start="1813" data-end="1828">AppController</code> created:</p>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="1839" data-end="1897"><div class="relative w-full mt-4 mb-1"><div class=""><div class="relative"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"><div class="border border-token-border-light border-radius-3xl corner-superellipse/1.1 rounded-3xl"><div class="h-full w-full border-radius-3xl bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary corner-superellipse/1.1 overflow-clip rounded-3xl lxnfua_clipPathFallback"><div class="sticky z-2 select-none top-(--sticky-padding-top)"><div class="flex w-full items-center justify-between py-1.5 ps-4 pe-1.5 font-sans md:ps-5 bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary"><div class="flex max-w-[75%] min-w-0 cursor-default items-center text-sm font-medium justify-self-start text-token-text-primary"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-sm me-2.5 shrink-0"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-ni7q5mnh.svg#e45ab3" fill="currentColor"></use></svg>Python</div><div class="flex flex-row items-center gap-0.5 justify-self-end"><button class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none py-2 text-sm font-medium hover:bg-black/5 dark:hover:bg-white/10 size-9 rounded-full px-2" aria-label="Copy" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-md"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-ni7q5mnh.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button><button class="btn relative group-focus-within/dialog:focus-visible:[outline-width:1.5px] group-focus-within/dialog:focus-visible:[outline-offset:2.5px] group-focus-within/dialog:focus-visible:[outline-style:solid] group-focus-within/dialog:focus-visible:[outline-color:var(--text-primary)] btn-ghost border-token-border-default ms-2 border font-sans" aria-label="Run code" type="button"><div class="flex w-full items-center justify-center gap-1.5"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-label="" class="-ms-0.5 icon"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-ni7q5mnh.svg#6ef7a4" fill="currentColor"></use></svg>Run</div></button></div></div></div><div class="pointer-events-none absolute inset-x-4 top-12 bottom-4"><div class="pointer-events-none sticky z-40 shrink-0 z-1!" style="top: calc(calc(var(--sticky-padding-top) + 48px) - 1px * 3); margin-bottom: calc(-4px); height: calc(4px); mask-image: linear-gradient(transparent 25%, white 75%);"><div class="sticky bg-token-border-light" style="top: calc(var(--sticky-padding-top) + 48px); height: 1px;"></div></div></div><div class="" style="transform: none;"><div class="relative z-0 flex max-w-full"><div id="code-block-viewer" dir="ltr" class="q9tKkq_viewer cm-editor z-10 light:cm-light dark:cm-light flex h-full w-full flex-col items-stretch ͼk ͼy"><div class="cm-scroller"><div class="cm-content q9tKkq_readonly"><span class="ͼt">self</span><span class="ͼn">.</span><span>trading_system </span><span class="ͼn">=</span><span> </span><span class="ͼt">SopotekTrading</span><span>(</span><span class="ͼt">config</span><span>)</span></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=""><div class="" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"></div></div></div></div></div></pre>
<p data-start="1899" data-end="1915">So it should be:</p>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="1917" data-end="1987"><div class="relative w-full mt-4 mb-1"><div class=""><div class="relative"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"><div class="border border-token-border-light border-radius-3xl corner-superellipse/1.1 rounded-3xl"><div class="h-full w-full border-radius-3xl bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary corner-superellipse/1.1 overflow-clip rounded-3xl lxnfua_clipPathFallback"><div class="sticky z-2 select-none top-(--sticky-padding-top)"><div class="flex w-full items-center justify-between py-1.5 ps-4 pe-1.5 font-sans md:ps-5 bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary"><div class="flex max-w-[75%] min-w-0 cursor-default items-center text-sm font-medium justify-self-start text-token-text-primary"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-sm me-2.5 shrink-0"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-ni7q5mnh.svg#e45ab3" fill="currentColor"></use></svg>Python</div><div class="flex flex-row items-center gap-0.5 justify-self-end"><button class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none py-2 text-sm font-medium hover:bg-black/5 dark:hover:bg-white/10 size-9 rounded-full px-2" aria-label="Copy" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-md"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-ni7q5mnh.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button><button class="btn relative group-focus-within/dialog:focus-visible:[outline-width:1.5px] group-focus-within/dialog:focus-visible:[outline-offset:2.5px] group-focus-within/dialog:focus-visible:[outline-style:solid] group-focus-within/dialog:focus-visible:[outline-color:var(--text-primary)] btn-ghost border-token-border-default ms-2 border font-sans" aria-label="Run code" type="button"><div class="flex w-full items-center justify-center gap-1.5"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-label="" class="-ms-0.5 icon"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-ni7q5mnh.svg#6ef7a4" fill="currentColor"></use></svg>Run</div></button></div></div></div><div class="pointer-events-none absolute inset-x-4 top-12 bottom-4"><div class="pointer-events-none sticky z-40 shrink-0 z-1!" style="top: calc(calc(var(--sticky-padding-top) + 48px) - 1px * 3); margin-bottom: calc(-4px); height: calc(4px); mask-image: linear-gradient(transparent 25%, white 75%);"><div class="sticky bg-token-border-light" style="top: calc(var(--sticky-padding-top) + 48px); height: 1px;"></div></div></div><div class="" style="transform: none;"><div class="relative z-0 flex max-w-full"><div id="code-block-viewer" dir="ltr" class="q9tKkq_viewer cm-editor z-10 light:cm-light dark:cm-light flex h-full w-full flex-col items-stretch ͼk ͼy"><div class="cm-scroller"><div class="cm-content q9tKkq_readonly"><span class="ͼt">loop</span><span class="ͼn">.</span><span>create_task(</span><span class="ͼt">self</span><span class="ͼn">.</span><span>controller</span><span class="ͼn">.</span><span>trading_system</span><span class="ͼn">.</span><span>start())</span></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=""><div class="" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"></div></div></div></div></div></pre>
<hr data-start="1989" data-end="1992">
<h1 data-section-id="9dkco7" data-start="1994" data-end="2047">✅ Corrected Critical Section of <code data-start="2028" data-end="2047">Terminal.__init__</code></h1>
<p data-start="2049" data-end="2095">Replace the beginning of <code data-start="2074" data-end="2084">__init__</code> with this:</p>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="2097" data-end="3532"><div class="relative w-full mt-4 mb-1"><div class=""><div class="relative"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"><div class="border border-token-border-light border-radius-3xl corner-superellipse/1.1 rounded-3xl"><div class="h-full w-full border-radius-3xl bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary corner-superellipse/1.1 overflow-clip rounded-3xl lxnfua_clipPathFallback"><div class="sticky z-2 select-none top-(--sticky-padding-top)"><div class="flex w-full items-center justify-between py-1.5 ps-4 pe-1.5 font-sans md:ps-5 bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary"><div class="flex max-w-[75%] min-w-0 cursor-default items-center text-sm font-medium justify-self-start text-token-text-primary"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-sm me-2.5 shrink-0"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-ni7q5mnh.svg#e45ab3" fill="currentColor"></use></svg>Python</div><div class="flex flex-row items-center gap-0.5 justify-self-end"><button class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none py-2 text-sm font-medium hover:bg-black/5 dark:hover:bg-white/10 size-9 rounded-full px-2" aria-label="Copy" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-md"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-ni7q5mnh.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button><button class="btn relative group-focus-within/dialog:focus-visible:[outline-width:1.5px] group-focus-within/dialog:focus-visible:[outline-offset:2.5px] group-focus-within/dialog:focus-visible:[outline-style:solid] group-focus-within/dialog:focus-visible:[outline-color:var(--text-primary)] btn-ghost border-token-border-default ms-2 border font-sans" aria-label="Run code" type="button"><div class="flex w-full items-center justify-center gap-1.5"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-label="" class="-ms-0.5 icon"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-ni7q5mnh.svg#6ef7a4" fill="currentColor"></use></svg>Run</div></button></div></div></div><div class="pointer-events-none absolute inset-x-4 top-12 bottom-4"><div class="pointer-events-none sticky z-40 shrink-0 z-1!" style="top: calc(calc(var(--sticky-padding-top) + 48px) - 1px * 3); margin-bottom: calc(-4px); height: calc(4px); mask-image: linear-gradient(transparent 25%, white 75%);"><div class="sticky bg-token-border-light" style="top: calc(var(--sticky-padding-top) + 48px); height: 1px;"></div></div></div><div class="" style="transform: none;"><div class="relative z-0 flex max-w-full"><div id="code-block-viewer" dir="ltr" class="q9tKkq_viewer cm-editor z-10 light:cm-light dark:cm-light flex h-full w-full flex-col items-stretch ͼk ͼy"><div class="cm-scroller"><div class="cm-content q9tKkq_readonly"><span class="ͼn">class</span><span> </span><span class="ͼs">Terminal</span><span>(</span><span class="ͼt">QMainWindow</span><span>):</span><br><br><span>    </span><span class="ͼt">logout_requested</span><span> </span><span class="ͼn">=</span><span> </span><span class="ͼt">Signal</span><span>()</span><br><span>    </span><span class="ͼt">ai_signal</span><span> </span><span class="ͼn">=</span><span> </span><span class="ͼt">Signal</span><span>(</span><span class="ͼt">dict</span><span>)</span><br><br><span>    </span><span class="ͼn">def</span><span> </span><span class="ͼt">__init__</span><span>(</span><span class="ͼt">self</span><span>, </span><span class="ͼt">controller</span><span>):</span><br><br><span>        </span><span class="ͼt">super</span><span>()</span><span class="ͼn">.</span><span>__init__(</span><span class="ͼt">controller</span><span>)</span><br><br><span>        </span><span class="ͼt">sys</span><span class="ͼn">.</span><span>excepthook </span><span class="ͼn">=</span><span> </span><span class="ͼt">global_exception_hook</span><br><br><span>        </span><span class="ͼt">self</span><span class="ͼn">.</span><span>controller </span><span class="ͼn">=</span><span> </span><span class="ͼt">controller</span><br><span>        </span><span class="ͼt">self</span><span class="ͼn">.</span><span>logger </span><span class="ͼn">=</span><span> </span><span class="ͼt">controller</span><span class="ͼn">.</span><span>logger</span><br><br><span>        </span><span class="ͼt">self</span><span class="ͼn">.</span><span>settings </span><span class="ͼn">=</span><span> </span><span class="ͼt">QSettings</span><span>(</span><span class="ͼr">"Sopotek"</span><span>, </span><span class="ͼr">"TradingPlatform"</span><span>)</span><br><br><span>        </span><span class="ͼt">self</span><span class="ͼn">.</span><span>symbols_table </span><span class="ͼn">=</span><span> </span><span class="ͼt">QTableWidget</span><span>()</span><br><br><span>        </span><span class="ͼt">self</span><span class="ͼn">.</span><span>risk_map </span><span class="ͼn">=</span><span> </span><span class="ͼq">None</span><br><span>        </span><span class="ͼt">self</span><span class="ͼn">.</span><span>auto_button </span><span class="ͼn">=</span><span> </span><span class="ͼt">QPushButton</span><span>()</span><br><br><span>        </span><span class="ͼt">self</span><span class="ͼn">.</span><span>historical_data </span><span class="ͼn">=</span><span> </span><span class="ͼt">controller</span><span class="ͼn">.</span><span>historical_data</span><br><br><span>        </span><span class="ͼt">self</span><span class="ͼn">.</span><span>confidence_data </span><span class="ͼn">=</span><span> []</span><br><br><span>        </span><span class="ͼn">if</span><span> </span><span class="ͼt">controller</span><span class="ͼn">.</span><span>symbols:</span><br><span>            </span><span class="ͼt">index</span><span> </span><span class="ͼn">=</span><span> </span><span class="ͼt">random</span><span class="ͼn">.</span><span>randint(</span><span class="ͼq">0</span><span>, </span><span class="ͼt">len</span><span>(</span><span class="ͼt">controller</span><span class="ͼn">.</span><span>symbols) </span><span class="ͼn">-</span><span> </span><span class="ͼq">1</span><span>)</span><br><span>            </span><span class="ͼt">self</span><span class="ͼn">.</span><span>symbol </span><span class="ͼn">=</span><span> </span><span class="ͼt">controller</span><span class="ͼn">.</span><span>symbols[</span><span class="ͼt">index</span><span>]</span><br><span>        </span><span class="ͼn">else</span><span>:</span><br><span>            </span><span class="ͼt">self</span><span class="ͼn">.</span><span>symbol </span><span class="ͼn">=</span><span> </span><span class="ͼr">"BTC/USDT"</span><br><br><span>        </span><span class="ͼt">self</span><span class="ͼn">.</span><span>MAX_LOG_ROWS </span><span class="ͼn">=</span><span> </span><span class="ͼq">500</span><br><span>        </span><span class="ͼt">self</span><span class="ͼn">.</span><span>current_timeframe </span><span class="ͼn">=</span><span> </span><span class="ͼr">"1m"</span><br><span>        </span><span class="ͼt">self</span><span class="ͼn">.</span><span>autotrading_enabled </span><span class="ͼn">=</span><span> </span><span class="ͼq">False</span><br><br><span>        </span><span class="ͼt">self</span><span class="ͼn">.</span><span>training_status </span><span class="ͼn">=</span><span> {}</span><br><br><span>        </span><span class="ͼt">self</span><span class="ͼn">.</span><span>heartbeat </span><span class="ͼn">=</span><span> </span><span class="ͼt">QLabel</span><span>(</span><span class="ͼr">"●"</span><span>)</span><br><span>        </span><span class="ͼt">self</span><span class="ͼn">.</span><span>heartbeat</span><span class="ͼn">.</span><span>setStyleSheet(</span><span class="ͼr">"color: green"</span><span>)</span><br><br><span>        </span><span class="ͼt">self</span><span class="ͼn">.</span><span>_setup_core()</span><br><span>        </span><span class="ͼt">self</span><span class="ͼn">.</span><span>_setup_ui()</span><br><span>        </span><span class="ͼt">self</span><span class="ͼn">.</span><span>_setup_panels()</span><br><span>        </span><span class="ͼt">self</span><span class="ͼn">.</span><span>_connect_signals()</span><br><span>        </span><span class="ͼt">self</span><span class="ͼn">.</span><span>_setup_spinner()</span><br><br><span>        </span><span class="ͼt">self</span><span class="ͼn">.</span><span>controller</span><span class="ͼn">.</span><span>symbols_signal</span><span class="ͼn">.</span><span>connect(</span><span class="ͼt">self</span><span class="ͼn">.</span><span>_update_symbols)</span><br><br><span>        </span><span class="ͼt">self</span><span class="ͼn">.</span><span>refresh_timer </span><span class="ͼn">=</span><span> </span><span class="ͼt">QTimer</span><span>()</span><br><span>        </span><span class="ͼt">self</span><span class="ͼn">.</span><span>refresh_timer</span><span class="ͼn">.</span><span>timeout</span><span class="ͼn">.</span><span>connect(</span><span class="ͼt">self</span><span class="ͼn">.</span><span>_refresh_terminal)</span><br><span>        </span><span class="ͼt">self</span><span class="ͼn">.</span><span>refresh_timer</span><span class="ͼn">.</span><span>start(</span><span class="ͼq">1000</span><span>)</span><br><br><span>        </span><span class="ͼt">self</span><span class="ͼn">.</span><span>ai_signal</span><span class="ͼn">.</span><span>connect(</span><span class="ͼt">self</span><span class="ͼn">.</span><span>_update_ai_signal)</span></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=""><div class="" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"></div></div></div></div></div></pre>
<hr data-start="3534" data-end="3537">
<h1 data-section-id="1k6oh9r" data-start="3539" data-end="3571">✅ Corrected AutoTrading Method</h1>
<p data-start="3573" data-end="3603">Replace <code data-start="3581" data-end="3602">_toggle_autotrading</code>:</p>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="3605" data-end="4333"><div class="relative w-full mt-4 mb-1"><div class=""><div class="relative"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"><div class="border border-token-border-light border-radius-3xl corner-superellipse/1.1 rounded-3xl"><div class="h-full w-full border-radius-3xl bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary corner-superellipse/1.1 overflow-clip rounded-3xl lxnfua_clipPathFallback"><div class="sticky z-2 select-none top-(--sticky-padding-top)"><div class="flex w-full items-center justify-between py-1.5 ps-4 pe-1.5 font-sans md:ps-5 bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary"><div class="flex max-w-[75%] min-w-0 cursor-default items-center text-sm font-medium justify-self-start text-token-text-primary"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-sm me-2.5 shrink-0"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-ni7q5mnh.svg#e45ab3" fill="currentColor"></use></svg>Python</div><div class="flex flex-row items-center gap-0.5 justify-self-end"><button class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none py-2 text-sm font-medium hover:bg-black/5 dark:hover:bg-white/10 size-9 rounded-full px-2" aria-label="Copy" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-md"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-ni7q5mnh.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button><button class="btn relative group-focus-within/dialog:focus-visible:[outline-width:1.5px] group-focus-within/dialog:focus-visible:[outline-offset:2.5px] group-focus-within/dialog:focus-visible:[outline-style:solid] group-focus-within/dialog:focus-visible:[outline-color:var(--text-primary)] btn-ghost border-token-border-default ms-2 border font-sans" aria-label="Run code" type="button"><div class="flex w-full items-center justify-center gap-1.5"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-label="" class="-ms-0.5 icon"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-ni7q5mnh.svg#6ef7a4" fill="currentColor"></use></svg>Run</div></button></div></div></div><div class="pointer-events-none absolute inset-x-4 top-12 bottom-4"><div class="pointer-events-none sticky z-40 shrink-0 z-1!" style="top: calc(calc(var(--sticky-padding-top) + 48px) - 1px * 3); margin-bottom: calc(-4px); height: calc(4px); mask-image: linear-gradient(transparent 25%, white 75%);"><div class="sticky bg-token-border-light" style="top: calc(var(--sticky-padding-top) + 48px); height: 1px;"></div></div></div><div class="" style="transform: none;"><div class="relative z-0 flex max-w-full"><div id="code-block-viewer" dir="ltr" class="q9tKkq_viewer cm-editor z-10 light:cm-light dark:cm-light flex h-full w-full flex-col items-stretch ͼk ͼy"><div class="cm-scroller"><div class="cm-content q9tKkq_readonly"><span class="ͼn">def</span><span> </span><span class="ͼt">_toggle_autotrading</span><span>(</span><span class="ͼt">self</span><span>):</span><br><br><span>    </span><span class="ͼt">self</span><span class="ͼn">.</span><span>autotrading_enabled </span><span class="ͼn">=</span><span> </span><span class="ͼn">not</span><span> </span><span class="ͼt">self</span><span class="ͼn">.</span><span>autotrading_enabled</span><br><br><span>    </span><span class="ͼn">if</span><span> </span><span class="ͼt">self</span><span class="ͼn">.</span><span>autotrading_enabled:</span><br><br><span>        </span><span class="ͼt">self</span><span class="ͼn">.</span><span>auto_button</span><span class="ͼn">.</span><span>setText(</span><span class="ͼr">"AutoTrading ON"</span><span>)</span><br><span>        </span><span class="ͼt">self</span><span class="ͼn">.</span><span>auto_button</span><span class="ͼn">.</span><span>setStyleSheet(</span><br><span>            </span><span class="ͼr">"background-color: green; color: white;"</span><br><span>        )</span><br><br><span>        </span><span class="ͼt">loop</span><span> </span><span class