<hr data-start="3469" data-end="3472">
<h1 data-section-id="2xi0ik" data-start="3474" data-end="3509">🚀 You Are Building Something Big</h1>
<p data-start="3511" data-end="3540">Your system already contains:</p>
<ul data-start="3542" data-end="3683">
<li data-section-id="pln477" data-start="3542" data-end="3562">
<p data-start="3544" data-end="3562">Broker abstraction</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="10jepqe" data-start="3563" data-end="3582">
