</li>
</ul>
<p data-start="3685" data-end="3758">That is basically <strong data-start="3703" data-end="3757">the architecture of professional trading platforms</strong>.</p>
<hr data-start="3760" data-end="3763">
<h1 data-section-id="1cjdffb" data-start="3765" data-end="3820">⚡ If you want, I can also show you something powerful</h1>
<p data-start="3822" data-end="3914">How to turn your <strong data-start="3839" data-end="3861">Sopotek Trading AI</strong> into a <strong data-start="3869" data-end="3908">multi-exchange institutional engine</strong> like:</p>
