Instead of processing symbols one by one, each symbol gets <strong data-start="159" data-end="190">its own asynchronous worker</strong> that:</p>
<ol data-start="198" data-end="279">
<li data-section-id="9k3vi8" data-start="198" data-end="215">
<p data-start="201" data-end="215">Fetches data</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="ufvxdp" data-start="216" data-end="238">
<p data-start="219" data-end="238">Runs the AI model</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="daa23x" data-start="239" data-end="261">
<p data-start="242" data-end="261">Generates signals</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="gw2dot" data-start="262" data-end="279">
<p data-start="265" data-end="279">Sends orders</p>
</li>
</ol>
<p data-start="281" data-end="358">This dramatically increases speed and scalability for <strong data-start="335" data-end="357">Sopotek Trading AI</strong>.</p>
<hr data-start="360" data-end="363">
<h1 data-section-id="wokt7a" data-start="365" data-end="421">🧠 Institutional Architecture (Parallel Symbol Engine)</h1>
<p data-start="423" data-end="455">Instead of this sequential loop:</p>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="457" data-end="602"><div class="relative w-full mt-4 mb-1"><div class=""><div class="relative"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"><div class="border border-token-border-light border-radius-3xl corner-superellipse/1.1 rounded-3xl"><div class="h-full w-full border-radius-3xl bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary corner-superellipse/1.1 overflow-clip rounded-3xl lxnfua_clipPathFallback"><div class="sticky z-2 select-none top-(--sticky-padding-top)"><div class="flex w-full items-center justify-between py-1.5 ps-4 pe-1.5 font-sans md:ps-5 bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary"><div class="flex max-w-[75%] min-w-0 cursor-default items-center text-sm font-medium justify-self-start text-token-text-primary"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-sm me-2.5 shrink-0"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-ni7q5mnh.svg#e45ab3" fill="currentColor"></use></svg>Python</div><div class="flex flex-row items-center gap-0.5 justify-self-end"><button class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none py-2 text-sm font-medium hover:bg-black/5 dark:hover:bg-white/10 size-9 rounded-full px-2" aria-label="Copy" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-md"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-ni7q5mnh.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button><button class="btn relative group-focus-within/dialog:focus-visible:[outline-width:1.5px] group-focus-within/dialog:focus-visible:[outline-offset:2.5px] group-focus-within/dialog:focus-visible:[outline-style:solid] group-focus-within/dialog:focus-visible:[outline-color:var(--text-primary)] btn-ghost border-token-border-default ms-2 border font-sans" aria-label="Run code" type="button"><div class="flex w-full items-center justify-center gap-1.5"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-label="" 