<p data-start="604" data-end="636">You create <strong data-start="615" data-end="635">parallel workers</strong>.</p>
<p data-start="638" data-end="651">Architecture:</p>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="653" data-end="957"><div class="relative w-full mt-4 mb-1"><div class=""><div class="relative"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"><div class="border border-token-border-light border-radius-3xl corner-superellipse/1.1 rounded-3xl"><div class="h-full w-full border-radius-3xl bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary corner-superellipse/1.1 overflow-clip rounded-3xl lxnfua_clipPathFallback"><div class="pointer-events-none absolute end-1.5 top-1 z-2 md:end-2 md:top-1"><button class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none pointer-events-auto py-2 text-sm font-medium hover:bg-black/5 dark:hover:bg-white/10 size-9 rounded-full px-2" aria-label="Copy" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-md"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-ni7q5mnh.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button></div><div class="pt-3" style="transform: none;"><div class="relative z-0 flex max-w-full"><div id="code-block-viewer" dir="ltr" class="q9tKkq_viewer cm-editor z-10 light:cm-light dark:cm-light flex h-full w-full flex-col items-stretch ͼk ͼy"><div class="cm-scroller"><div class="cm-content q9tKkq_readonly"><span>SopotekTrading</span><br><span>        │</span><br><span>        │</span><br><span>        ▼</span><br><span>Symbol Orchestrator</span><br><span>        │</span><br><span> ┌──────┼─────────┐</span><br><span> │      │         │</span><br><span> ▼      ▼         ▼</span><br><span>BTC Worker  ETH Worker  SOL Worker</span><br><span> │      │         │</span><br><span> ▼      ▼         ▼</span><br><span>AI Model  AI Model  AI Model</span><br><span> │      │         │</span><br><span> ▼      ▼         ▼</span><br><span>Execution Manager</span></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=""><div class="" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"></div></div></div></div></div></pre>
<p data-start="959" data-end="994">Each symbol runs <strong data-start="976" data-end="993">independently</strong>.</p>
<hr data-start="996" data-end="999">
<h1 data-section-id="13x3pus" data-start="1001" data-end="1034">⚡ Step 1 — Create Symbol Worker</h1>
<p data-start="1036" data-end="1079">Create a worker that trades <strong data-start="1064" data-end="1078">one symbol</strong>.</p>
