<h1 data-section-id="dmeyrm" data-start="2602" data-end="2648">4️⃣ Improve Credential Storage (Recommended)</h1>
<p data-start="2650" data-end="2710">Inside <code data-start="2657" data-end="2676">CredentialManager</code>, ensure accounts are stored like:</p>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="2712" data-end="2744"><div class="relative w-full mt-4 mb-1"><div class=""><div class="relative"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"><div class="border border-token-border-light border-radius-3xl corner-superellipse/1.1 rounded-3xl"><div class="h-full w-full border-radius-3xl bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary corner-superellipse/1.1 overflow-clip rounded-3xl lxnfua_clipPathFallback"><div class="pointer-events-none absolute end-1.5 top-1 z-2 md:end-2 md:top-1"><button class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none pointer-events-auto py-2 text-sm font-medium hover:bg-black/5 dark:hover:bg-white/10 size-9 rounded-full px-2" aria-label="Copy" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-md"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-ni7q5mnh.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button></div><div class="pt-3" style="transform: none;"><div class="relative z-0 flex max-w-full"><div id="code-block-viewer" dir="ltr" class="q9tKkq_viewer cm-editor z-10 light:cm-light dark:cm-light flex h-full w-full flex-col items-stretch ͼk ͼy"><div class="cm-scroller"><div class="cm-content q9tKkq_readonly"><span>~/.sopotek/accounts.json</span></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=""><div class="" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"></div></div></div></div></div></pre>
<p data-start="2746" data-end="2764">Example structure:</p>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="2766" data-end="2994"><div class="relative w-full mt-4 mb-1"><div class=""><div class="relative"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"><div class="border border-token-border-light border-radius-3xl corner-superellipse/1.1 rounded-3xl"><div class="h-full w-full border-radius-3xl bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary corner-superellipse/1.1 overflow-clip rounded-3xl lxnfua_clipPathFallback"><div class="sticky z-2 select-none top-(--sticky-padding-top)"><div class="flex w-full items-center justify-between py-1.5 ps-4 pe-1.5 font-sans md:ps-5 bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary"><div class="flex max-w-[75%] min-w-0 cursor-default items-center text-sm font-medium justify-self-start text-token-text-primary"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-sm me-2.5 shrink-0"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-ni7q5mnh.svg#e45ab3" fill="currentColor"></use></svg>JSON</div><div class="flex flex-row items-center gap-0.5 justify-self-end"><button class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none py-2 text-sm font-medium hover:bg-black/5 dark:hover:bg-white/10 size-9 rounded-full px-2" aria-label="Copy" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-md"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-ni7q5mnh.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button></div></div></div><div class="pointer-events-none absolute inset-x-4 top-12 bottom-4"><div class="pointer-events-none sticky z-40 shrink-0 z-1!" style="top: calc(calc(var(--sticky-padding-top) + 48px) - 1px * 3); margin-bottom: calc(-4px); height: calc(4px); mask-image: linear-gradient(transparent 25%, white 75%);"><div class="sticky bg-token-border-light" style="top: calc(var(--sticky-padding-top) + 48px); height: 1px;"></div></div></div><div class="" style="transform: none;"><div class="relative z-0 flex max-w-full"><div id="code-block-viewer" dir="ltr" class="q9tKkq_viewer cm-editor z-10 light:cm-light dark:cm-light flex h-full w-full flex-col items-stretch ͼk ͼy"><div class="cm-scroller"><div class="cm-content q9tKkq_readonly"><span>{</span><br><span> "binance_abcd12": {</span><br><span>  "broker": {</span><br><span>   "type": </span><span class="ͼr">"crypto"</span><span>,</span><br><span>   "exchange": </span><span class="ͼr">"binance"</span><span>,</span><br><span>   "api_key": </span><span class="ͼr">"..."</span><span>,</span><br><span>   "secret": </span><span class="ͼr">"..."</span><span>,</span><br><span>   "mode": </span><span class="ͼr">"live"</span><br><span>  },</span><br><span>  "risk": {</span><br><span>   "risk_percent": </span><span class="ͼq">2</span><br><span>  },</span><br><span>  "strategy": </span><span class="ͼr">"EMA_CROSS"</span><br><span> }</span><br><span>}</span></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=""><div class="" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"></div></div></div></div></div></pre>
<hr data-start="2996" data-end="2999">
<h1 data-section-id="mv1a3q" data-start="3001" data-end="3057">5️⃣ Optional: Make the Logo Always Load (Professional)</h1>
<p data-start="3059" data-end="3113">Sometimes relative paths break. Use <strong data-start="3095" data-end="3112">absolute path</strong>:</p>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="3115" data-end="3279"><div class="relative w-full mt-4 mb-1"><div class=""><div class="relative"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"><div class="border border-token-border-light border-radius-3xl corner-superellipse/1.1 rounded-3xl"><div class="h-full w-full border-radius-3xl bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary corner-superellipse/1.1 overflow-clip rounded-3xl lxnfua_clipPathFallback"><div class="sticky z-2 select-none top-(--sticky-padding-top)"><div class="flex w-full items-center justify-between py-1.5 ps-4 pe-1.5 font-sans md:ps-5 bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary"><div class="flex max-w-[75%] min-w-0 cursor-default items-center text-sm font-medium justify-self-start text-token-text-primary"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-sm me-2.5 shrink-0"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-ni7q5mnh.svg#e45ab3" fill="currentColor"></use></svg>Python</div><div class="flex flex-row items-center gap-0.5 justify-self-end"><button class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none py-2 text-sm font-medium hover:bg-black/5 dark:hover:bg-white/10 size-9 rounded-full px-2" aria-label="Copy" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-md"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-ni7q5mnh.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button><button class="btn relative group-focus-within/dialog:focus-visible:[outline-width:1.5px] group-focus-within/dialog:focus-visible:[outline-offset:2.5px] group-focus-within/dialog:focus-visible:[outline-style:solid] group-focus-within/dialog:focus-visible:[outline-color:var(--text-primary)] btn-ghost border-token-border-default ms-2 border font-sans" aria-label="Run code" type="button"><div class="flex w-full items-center justify-center gap-1.5"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-label="" class="-ms-0.5 icon"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-ni7q5mnh.svg#6ef7a4" fill="currentColor"></use></svg>Run</div></button></div></div></div><div class="pointer-events-none absolute inset-x-4 top-12 bottom-4"><div class="pointer-events-none sticky z-40 shrink-0 z-1!" style="top: calc(calc(var(--sticky-padding-top) + 48px) - 1px * 3); margin-bottom: calc(-4px); height: calc(4px); mask-image: linear-gradient(transparent 25%, white 75%);"><div class="sticky bg-token-border-light" style="top: calc(var(--sticky-padding-top) + 48px); height: 1px;"></div></div></div><div class="" style="transform: none;"><div class="relative z-0 flex max-w-full"><div id="code-block-viewer" dir="ltr" class="q9tKkq_viewer cm-editor z-10 light:cm-light dark:cm-light flex h-full w-full flex-col items-stretch ͼk ͼy"><div class="cm-scroller"><div class="cm-content q9tKkq_readonly"><span class="ͼn">import</span><span> </span><span class="ͼt">os</span><br><br><span class="ͼt">base_dir</span><span> </span><span class="ͼn">=</span><span> </span><span class="ͼt">os</span><span class="ͼn">.</span><span>path</span><span class="ͼn">.</span><span>dirname(</span><span class="ͼt">os</span><span class="ͼn">.</span><span>path</span><span class="ͼn">.</span><span>dirname(</span><span class="ͼt">__file__</span><span>))</span><br><span class="ͼt">logo_path</span><span> </span><span class="ͼn">=</span><span> </span><span class="ͼt">os</span><span class="ͼn">.</span><span>path</span><span class="ͼn">.</span><span>join(</span><span class="ͼt">base_dir</span><span>, </span><span class="ͼr">"assets"</span><span>, </span><span class="ͼr">"logo.png"</span><span>)</span><br><br><span class="ͼt">pixmap</span><span> </span><span class="ͼn">=</span><span> </span><span class="ͼt">QPixmap</span><span>(</span><span class="ͼt">logo_path</span><span>)</span></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=""><div class="" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"></div></div></div></div></div></pre>
<p data-start="3281" data-end="3315">This guarantees it loads anywhere.</p>
