<p data-start="3496" data-end="3513">💡 <strong data-start="3499" data-end="3513">Suggestion</strong></p>
<p data-start="3515" data-end="3650">Your dashboard is already very close to something <strong data-start="3565" data-end="3581">professional</strong>. The next upgrade that will make it look <strong data-start="3623" data-end="3646">institutional-grade</strong> is:</p>
