<h1 data-section-id="xw6n9q" data-start="301" data-end="360">🚨 Problem 1 — Wrong Variable (<code data-start="334" data-end="342">broker</code> vs <code data-start="346" data-end="359">self.broker</code>)</h1>
<p data-start="362" data-end="404">Inside <code data-start="369" data-end="393">_load_selected_account</code> you wrote:</p>
