<p data-start="674" data-end="711">So Python should use <strong data-start="695" data-end="710">self.broker</strong>.</p>
<h3 data-section-id="1nef3pw" data-start="713" data-end="722">✅ Fix</h3>
<p data-start="724" data-end="750">Replace that section with:</p>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="752" data-end="1060"><div class="relative w-full mt-4 mb-1"><div class=""><div class="relative"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"><div class="border border-token-border-light border-radius-3xl corner-superellipse/1.1 rounded-3xl"><div class="h-full w-full border-radius-3xl bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary corner-superellipse/1.1 overflow-clip rounded-3xl lxnfua_clipPathFallback"><div class="sticky z-2 select-none top-(--sticky-padding-top)"><div class="flex w-full items-center justify-between py-1.5 ps-4 pe-1.5 font-sans md:ps-5 bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary"><div class="flex max-w-[75%] min-w-0 cursor-default items-center text-sm font-medium justify-self-start text-token-text-primary"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-sm me-2.5 shrink-0"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-ni7q5mnh.svg#e45ab3" fill="currentColor"></use></svg>Python</div><div class="flex flex-row items-center gap-0.5 justify-self-end"><button class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none py-2 text-sm font-medium hover:bg-black/5 dark:hover:bg-white/10 size-9 rounded-full px-2" aria-label="Copy" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-md"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-ni7q5mnh.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button><button class="btn relative group-focus-within/dialog:focus-visible:[outline-width:1.5px] group-focus-within/dialog:focus-visible:[outline-offset:2.5px] group-focus-within/dialog:focus-visible:[outline-style:solid] group-focus-within/dialog:focus-visible:[outline-color:var(--text-primary)] btn-ghost border-token-border-default ms-2 border font-sans" aria-label="Run code" type="button"><div class="flex w-full items-center justify-center gap-1.5"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-label="" class="-ms-0.5 icon"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-ni7q5mnh.svg#6ef7a4" fill="currentColor"></use></svg>Run</div></button></div></div></div><div class="pointer-events-none absolute inset-x-4 top-12 bottom-4"><div class="pointer-events-none sticky z-40 shrink-0 z-1!" style="top: calc(calc(var(--sticky-padding-top) + 48px) - 1px * 3); margin-bottom: calc(-4px); height: calc(4px); mask-image: linear-gradient(transparent 25%, white 75%);"><div class="sticky bg-token-border-light" style="top: calc(var(--sticky-padding-top) + 48px); height: 1px;"></div></div></div><div class="" style="transform: none;"><div class="relative z-0 flex max-w-full"><div id="code-block-viewer" dir="ltr" class="q9tKkq_viewer cm-editor z-10 light:cm-light dark:cm-light flex h-full w-full flex-col items-stretch ͼk ͼy"><div class="cm-scroller"><div class="cm-content q9tKkq_readonly"><span class="ͼt">broker</span><span> </span><span class="ͼn">=</span><span> </span><span class="ͼt">creds</span><span>[</span><span class="ͼr">"broker"</span><span>]</span><br><br><span class="ͼt">self</span><span class="ͼn">.</span><span>exchange_type_box</span><span class="ͼn">.</span><span>setCurrentText(</span><span class="ͼt">broker</span><span>[</span><span class="ͼr">"type"</span><span>])</span><br><span class="ͼt">self</span><span class="ͼn">.</span><span>exchange_box</span><span class="ͼn">.</span><span>setCurrentText(</span><span class="ͼt">broker</span><span>[</span><span class="ͼr">"exchange"</span><span>])</span><br><br><span class="ͼt">self</span><span class="ͼn">.</span><span>api_input</span><span class="ͼn">.</span><span>setText(</span><span class="ͼt">broker</span><span class="ͼn">.</span><span>get(</span><span class="ͼr">"api_key"</span><span>, </span><span class="ͼr">""</span><span>))</span><br><span class="ͼt">self</span><span class="ͼn">.</span><span>secret_input</span><span class="ͼn">.</span><span>setText(</span><span class="ͼt">broker</span><span class="ͼn">.</span><span>get(</span><span class="ͼr">"secret"</span><span>, </span><span class="ͼr">""</span><span>))</span><br><br><span class="ͼt">self</span><span class="ͼn">.</span><span>mode_box</span><span class="ͼn">.</span><span>setCurrentText(</span><span class="ͼt">broker</span><span class="ͼn">.</span><span>get(</span><span class="ͼr">"mode"</span><span>, </span><span class="ͼr">"paper"</span><span>))</span></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=""><div class="" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"></div></div></div></div></div></pre>
<hr data-start="1062" data-end="1065">
<h1 data-section-id="1bfzg7h" data-start="1067" data-end="1102">🚨 Problem 2 — Wrong Object Saved</h1>
<p data-start="1104" data-end="1124">You are saving this:</p>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="1126" data-end="1183"><div class="relative w-full mt-4 mb-1"><div class=""><div class="relative"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"><div class="border border-token-border-light border-radius-3xl corner-superellipse/1.1 rounded-3xl"><div class="h-full w-full border-radius-3xl bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary corner-superellipse/1.1 overflow-clip rounded-3xl lxnfua_clipPathFallback"><div class="sticky z-2 select-none top-(--sticky-padding-top)"><div class="flex w-full items-center justify-between py-1.5 ps-4 pe-1.5 font-sans md:ps-5 bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary"><div class="flex max-w-[75%] min-w-0 cursor-default items-center text-sm font-medium justify-self-start text-token-text-primary"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-sm me-2.5 shrink-0"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-ni7q5mnh.svg#e45ab3" fill="currentColor"></use></svg>Python</div><div class="flex flex-row items-center gap-0.5 justify-self-end"><button class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none py-2 text-sm font-medium hover:bg-black/5 dark:hover:bg-white/10 size-9 rounded-full px-2" aria-label="Copy" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-md"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-ni7q5mnh.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button><button class="btn relative group-focus-within/dialog:focus-visible:[outline-width:1.5px] group-focus-within/dialog:focus-visible:[outline-offset:2.5px] group-focus-within/dialog:focus-visible:[outline-style:solid] group-focus-within/dialog:focus-visible:[outline-color:var(--text-primary)] btn-ghost border-token-border-default ms-2 border font-sans" aria-label="Run code" type="button"><div class="flex w-full items-center justify-center gap-1.5"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-label="" class="-ms-0.5 icon"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-ni7q5mnh.svg#6ef7a4" fill="currentColor"></use></svg>Run</div></button></div></div></div><div class="pointer-events-none absolute inset-x-4 top-12 bottom-4"><div class="pointer-events-none sticky z-40 shrink-0 z-1!" style="top: calc(calc(var(--sticky-padding-top) + 48px) - 1px * 3); margin-bottom: calc(-4px); height: calc(4px); mask-image: linear-gradient(transparent 25%, white 75%);"><div class="sticky bg-token-border-light" style="top: calc(var(--sticky-padding-top) + 48px); height: 1px;"></div></div></div><div class="" style="transform: none;"><div class="relative z-0 flex max-w-full"><div id="code-block-viewer" dir="ltr" class="q9tKkq_viewer cm-editor z-10 light:cm-light dark:cm-light flex h-full w-full flex-col items-stretch ͼk ͼy"><div class="cm-scroller"><div class="cm-content q9tKkq_readonly"><span class="ͼt">config</span><span> </span><span class="ͼn">=</span><span> </span><span class="ͼt">AppConfig</span><span>(</span><br><span>    </span><span class="ͼt">broker</span><span class="ͼn">=</span><span class="ͼt">self</span><span class="ͼn">.</span><span>broker,</span></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=""><div class="" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"></div></div></div></div></div></pre>
<p data-start="1185" data-end="1250">But <code data-start="1189" data-end="1202">self.broker</code> is a <strong data-start="1208" data-end="1229">CCXTBroker object</strong>, not <code data-start="1235" data-end="1249">BrokerConfig</code>.</p>
<p data-start="1252" data-end="1270">When you later do:</p>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="1272" data-end="1299"><div class="relative w-full mt-4 mb-1"><div class=""><div class="relative"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"><div class="border border-token-border-light border-radius-3xl corner-superellipse/1.1 rounded-3xl"><div class="h-full w-full border-radius-3xl bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary corner-superellipse/1.1 overflow-clip rounded-3xl lxnfua_clipPathFallback"><div class="sticky z-2 select-none top-(--sticky-padding-top)"><div class="flex w-full items-center justify-between py-1.5 ps-4 pe-1.5 font-sans md:ps-5 bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary"><div class="flex max-w-[75%] min-w-0 cursor-default items-center text-sm font-medium justify-self-start text-token-text-primary"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-sm me-2.5 shrink-0"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-ni7q5mnh.svg#e45ab3" fill="currentColor"></use></svg>Python</div><div class="flex flex-row items-center gap-0.5 justify-self-end"><button class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none py-2 text-sm font-medium hover:bg-black/5 dark:hover:bg-white/10 size-9 rounded-full px-2" aria-label="Copy" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-md"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-ni7q5mnh.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button><button class="btn relative group-focus-within/dialog:focus-visible:[outline-width:1.5px] group-focus-within/dialog:focus-visible:[outline-offset:2.5px] group-focus-within/dialog:focus-visible:[outline-style:solid] group-focus-within/dialog:focus-visible:[outline-color:var(--text-primary)] btn-ghost border-token-border-default ms-2 border font-sans" aria-label="Run code" type="button"><div class="flex w-full items-center justify-center gap-1.5"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-label="" class="-ms-0.5 icon"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-ni7q5mnh.svg#6ef7a4" fill="currentColor"></use></svg>Run</div></button></div></div></div><div class="pointer-events-none absolute inset-x-4 top-12 bottom-4"><div class="pointer-events-none sticky z-40 shrink-0 z-1!" style="top: calc(calc(var(--sticky-padding-top) + 48px) - 1px * 3); margin-bottom: calc(-4px); height: calc(4px); mask-image: linear-gradient(transparent 25%, white 75%);"><div class="sticky bg-token-border-light" style="top: calc(var(--sticky-padding-top) + 48px); height: 1px;"></div></div></div><div class="" style="transform: none;"><div class="relative z-0 flex max-w-full"><div id="code-block-viewer" dir="ltr" class="q9tKkq_viewer cm-editor z-10 light:cm-light dark:cm-light flex h-full w-full flex-col items-stretch ͼk ͼy"><div class="cm-scroller"><div class="cm-content q9tKkq_readonly"><span class="ͼt">config</span><span class="ͼn">.</span><span>dict()</span></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=""><div class="" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"></div></div></div></div></div></pre>
<p data-start="1301" data-end="1361">Pydantic <strong data-start="1310" data-end="1360">cannot serialize the broker instance correctly</strong>.</p>
<p data-start="1363" data-end="1393">This breaks credential saving.</p>
<hr data-start="1395" data-end="1398">
<h2 data-section-id="rf6ttd" data-start="1400" data-end="1416">✅ Correct Way</h2>
<p data-start="1418" data-end="1465">Save <strong data-start="1423" data-end="1439">BrokerConfig</strong>, not the broker instance.</p>
<p data-start="1467" data-end="1501">Replace <code data-start="1475" data-end="1490">_on_connect()</code> with this:</p>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="1503" data-end="1951"><div class="relative w-full mt-4 mb-1"><div class=""><div class="relative"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"><div class="border border-token-border-light border-radius-3xl corner-superellipse/1.1 rounded-3xl"><div class="h-full w-full border-radius-3xl bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary corner-superellipse/1.1 overflow-clip rounded-3xl lxnfua_clipPathFallback"><div class="sticky z-2 select-none top-(--sticky-padding-top)"><div class="flex w-full items-center justify-between py-1.5 ps-4 pe-1.5 font-sans md:ps-5 bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary"><div class="flex max-w-[75%] min-w-0 cursor-default items-center text-sm font-medium justify-self-start text-token-text-primary"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-sm me-2.5 shrink-0"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-ni7q5mnh.svg#e45ab3" fill="currentColor"></use></svg>Python</div><div class="flex flex-row items-center gap-0.5 justify-self-end"><button class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none py-2 text-sm font-medium hover:bg-black/5 dark:hover:bg-white/10 size-9 rounded-full px-2" aria-label="Copy" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-md"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-ni7q5mnh.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button><button class="btn relative group-focus-within/dialog:focus-visible:[outline-width:1.5px] group-focus-within/dialog:focus-visible:[outline-offset:2.5px] group-focus-within/dialog:focus-visible:[outline-style:solid] group-focus-within/dialog:focus-visible:[outline-color:var(--text-primary)] btn-ghost border-token-border-default ms-2 border font-sans" aria-label="Run code" type="button"><div class="flex w-full items-center justify-center gap-1.5"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-label="" class="-ms-0.5 icon"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-ni7q5mnh.svg#6ef7a4" fill="currentColor"></use></svg>Run</div></button></div></div></div><div class="pointer-events-none absolute inset-x-4 top-12 bottom-4"><div class="pointer-events-none sticky z-40 shrink-0 z-1!" style="top: calc(calc(var(--sticky-padding-top) + 48px) - 1px * 3); margin-bottom: calc(-4px); height: calc(4px); mask-image: linear-gradient(transparent 25%, white 75%);"><div class="sticky bg-token-border-light" style="top: calc(var(--sticky-padding-top) + 48px); height: 1px;"></div></div></div><div class="" style="transform: none;"><div class="relative z-0 flex max-w-full"><div id="code-block-viewer" dir="ltr" class="q9tKkq_viewer cm-editor z-10 light:cm-light dark:cm-light flex h-full w-full flex-col items-stretch ͼk ͼy"><div class="cm-scroller"><div class="cm-content q9tKkq_readonly"><span class="ͼt">broker_config</span><span> </span><span class="ͼn">=</span><span> </span><span class="ͼt">BrokerConfig</span><span>(</span><br><span>    </span><span class="ͼt">type</span><span class="ͼn">=</span><span class="ͼt">self</span><span class="ͼn">.</span><span>exchange_type_box</span><span class="ͼn">.</span><span>currentText(),</span><br><span>    </span><span class="ͼt">exchange</span><span class="ͼn">=</span><span class="ͼt">exchange</span><span>,</span><br><span>    </span><span class="ͼt">mode</span><span class="ͼn">=</span><span class="ͼt">self</span><span class="ͼn">.</span><span>mode_box</span><span class="ͼn">.</span><span>currentText(),</span><br><span>    </span><span class="ͼt">api_key</span><span class="ͼn">=</span><span class="ͼt">api_key</span><span>,</span><br><span>    </span><span class="ͼt">secret</span><span class="ͼn">=</span><span class="ͼt">secret</span><br><span>)</span><br><br><span class="ͼl"># create broker instance</span><br><span class="ͼt">self</span><span class="ͼn">.</span><span>broker </span><span class="ͼn">=</span><span> </span><span class="ͼt">BrokerFactory</span><span class="ͼn">.</span><span>create(</span><span class="ͼt">broker_config</span><span>)</span><br><br><span class="ͼt">config</span><span> </span><span class="ͼn">=</span><span> </span><span class="ͼt">AppConfig</span><span>(</span><br><span>    </span><span class="ͼt">broker</span><span class="ͼn">=</span><span class="ͼt">broker_config</span><span>,</span><br><span>    </span><span class="ͼt">risk</span><span class="ͼn">=</span><span class="ͼt">RiskConfig</span><span>(</span><span class="ͼt">risk_percent</span><span class="ͼn">=</span><span class="ͼt">self</span><span class="ͼn">.</span><span>risk_input</span><span class="ͼn">.</span><span>value()),</span><br><span>    </span><span class="ͼt">system</span><span class="ͼn">=</span><span class="ͼt">SystemConfig</span><span>(),</span><br><span>    </span><span class="ͼt">strategy</span><span class="ͼn">=</span><span class="ͼt">self</span><span class="ͼn">.</span><span>strategy_box</span><span class="ͼn">.</span><span>currentText()</span><br><span>)</span></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=""><div class="" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"></div></div></div></div></div></pre>
<p data-start="1953" data-end="1957">Now:</p>
<p data-start="1959" data-end="2032">✔ broker instance used by system<br data-start="1991" data-end="1994">
✔ broker config saved in credentials</p>
<hr data-start="2034" data-end="2037">
<h1 data-section-id="2q88sl" data-start="2039" data-end="2097">🚨 Problem 3 — Loading Exchanges Before Setting Exchange</h1>
<p data-start="2099" data-end="2130">When loading an account you do:</p>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="2132" data-end="2252"><div class="relative w-full mt-4 mb-1"><div class=""><div class="relative"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"><div class="border border-token-border-light border-radius-3xl corner-superellipse/1.1 rounded-3xl"><div class="h-full w-full border-radius-3xl bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary corner-superellipse/1.1 overflow-clip rounded-3xl lxnfua_clipPathFallback"><div class="sticky z-2 select-none top-(--sticky-padding-top)"><div class="flex w-full items-center justify-between py-1.5 ps-4 pe-1.5 font-sans md:ps-5 bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary"><div class="flex max-w-[75%] min-w-0 cursor-default items-center text-sm font-medium justify-self-start text-token-text-primary"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-sm me-2.5 shrink-0"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-ni7q5mnh.svg#e45ab3" fill="currentColor"></use></svg>Python</div><div class="flex flex-row items-center gap-0.5 justify-self-end"><button class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none py-2 text-sm font-medium hover:bg-black/5 dark:hover:bg-white/10 size-9 rounded-full px-2" aria-label="Copy" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-md"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-ni7q5mnh.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button><button class="btn relative group-focus-within/dialog:focus-visible:[outline-width:1.5px] group-focus-within/dialog:focus-visible:[outline-offset:2.5px] group-focus-within/dialog:focus-visible:[outline-style:solid] group-focus-within/dialog:focus-visible:[outline-color:var(--text-primary)] btn-ghost border-token-border-default ms-2 border font-sans" aria-label="Run code" type="button"><div class="flex w-full items-center justify-center gap-1.5"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-label="" class="-ms-0.5 icon"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-ni7q5mnh.svg#6ef7a4" fill="currentColor"></use></svg>Run</div></button></div></div></div><div class="pointer-events-none absolute inset-x-4 top-12 bottom-4"><div class="pointer-events-none sticky z-40 shrink-0 z-1!" style="top: calc(calc(var(--sticky-padding-top) + 48px) - 1px * 3); margin-bottom: calc(-4px); height: calc(4px); mask-image: linear-gradient(transparent 25%, white 75%);"><div class="sticky bg-token-border-light" style="top: calc(var(--sticky-padding-top) + 48px); height: 1px;"></div></div></div><div class="" style="transform: none;"><div class="relative z-0 flex max-w-full"><div id="code-block-viewer" dir="ltr" class="q9tKkq_viewer cm-editor z-10 light:cm-light dark:cm-light flex h-full w-full flex-col items-stretch ͼk ͼy"><div class="cm-scroller"><div class="cm-content q9tKkq_readonly"><span class="ͼt">self</span><span class="ͼn">.</span><span>exchange_type_box</span><span class="ͼn">.</span><span>setCurrentText(</span><span class="ͼt">broker</span><span>[</span><span class="ͼr">"type"</span><span>])</span><br><span class="ͼt">self</span><span class="ͼn">.</span><span>exchange_box</span><span class="ͼn">.</span><span>setCurrentText(</span><span class="ͼt">broker</span><span>[</span><span class="ͼr">"exchange"</span><span>])</span></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=""><div class="" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"></div></div></div></div></div></pre>
<p data-start="2254" data-end="2351">But when <code data-start="2263" data-end="2282">exchange_type_box</code> changes, <code data-start="2292" data-end="2317">_update_exchange_list()</code> runs and <strong data-start="2327" data-end="2350">clears exchange_box</strong>.</p>
<p data-start="2353" data-end="2380">So the exchange gets reset.</p>
<hr data-start="2382" data-end="2385">
<h3 data-section-id="1nef3pw" data-start="2387" data-end="2396">✅ Fix</h3>
<p data-start="2398" data-end="2435">Force update before setting exchange:</p>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="2437" data-end="2628"><div class="relative w-full mt-4 mb-1"><div class=""><div class="relative"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"><div class="border border-token-border-light border-radius-3xl corner-superellipse/1.1 rounded-3xl"><div class="h-full w-full border-radius-3xl bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary corner-superellipse/1.1 overflow-clip rounded-3xl lxnfua_clipPathFallback"><div class="sticky z-2 select-none top-(--sticky-padding-top)"><div class="flex w-full items-center justify-between py-1.5 ps-4 pe-1.5 font-sans md:ps-5 bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary"><div class="flex max-w-[75%] min-w-0 cursor-default items-center text-sm font-medium justify-self-start text-token-text-primary"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-sm me-2.5 shrink-0"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-ni7q5mnh.svg#e45ab3" fill="currentColor"></use></svg>Python</div><div class="flex flex-row items-center gap-0.5 justify-self-end"><button class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none py-2 text-sm font-medium hover:bg-black/5 dark:hover:bg-white/10 size-9 rounded-full px-2" aria-label="Copy" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-md"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-ni7q5mnh.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button><button class="btn relative group-focus-within/dialog:focus-visible:[outline-width:1.5px] group-focus-within/dialog:focus-visible:[outline-offset:2.5px] group-focus-within/dialog:focus-visible:[outline-style:solid] group-focus-within/dialog:focus-visible:[outline-color:var(--text-primary)] btn-ghost border-token-border-default ms-2 border font-sans" aria-label="Run code" type="button"><div class="flex w-full items-center justify-center gap-1.5"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-label="" class="-ms-0.5 icon"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-ni7q5mnh.svg#6ef7a4" fill="currentColor"></use></svg>Run</div></button></div></div></div><div class="pointer-events-none absolute inset-x-4 top-12 bottom-4"><div class="pointer-events-none sticky z-40 shrink-0 z-1!" style="top: calc(calc(var(--sticky-padding-top) + 48px) - 1px * 3); margin-bottom: calc(-4px); height: calc(4px); mask-image: linear-gradient(transparent 25%, white 75%);"><div class="sticky bg-token-border-light" style="top: calc(var(--sticky-padding-top) + 48px); height: 1px;"></div></div></div><div class="" style="transform: none;"><div class="relative z-0 flex max-w-full"><div id="code-block-viewer" dir="ltr" class="q9tKkq_viewer cm-editor z-10 light:cm-light dark:cm-light flex h-full w-full flex-col items-stretch ͼk ͼy"><div class="cm-scroller"><div class="cm-content q9tKkq_readonly"><span class="ͼt">broker</span><span> </span><span class="ͼn">=</span><span> </span><span class="ͼt">creds</span><span>[</span><span class="ͼr">"broker"</span><span>]</span><br><br><span class="ͼt">self</span><span class="ͼn">.</span><span>exchange_type_box</span><span class="ͼn">.</span><span>setCurrentText(</span><span class="ͼt">broker</span><span>[</span><span class="ͼr">"type"</span><span>])</span><br><br><span class="ͼt">self</span><span class="ͼn">.</span><span>_update_exchange_list(</span><span class="ͼt">broker</span><span>[</span><span class="ͼr">"type"</span><span>])</span><br><br><span class="ͼt">self</span><span class="ͼn">.</span><span>exchange_box</span><span class="ͼn">.</span><span>setCurrentText(</span><span class="ͼt">broker</span><span>[</span><span class="ͼr">"exchange"</span><span>])</span></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=""><div class="" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"></div></div></div></div></div></pre>
<hr data-start="2630" data-end="2633">
<h1 data-section-id="lesqex" data-start="2635" data-end="2671">⭐ Correct <code data-start="2647" data-end="2671">_load_selected_account</code></h1>
<p data-start="2673" data-end="2724">Replace the whole function with this clean version:</p>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="2726" data-end="3505"><div class="relative w-full mt-4 mb-1"><div class=""><div class="relative"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"><div class="border border-token-border-light border-radius-3xl corner-superellipse/1.1 rounded-3xl"><div class="h-full w-full border-radius-3xl bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary corner-superellipse/1.1 overflow-clip rounded-3xl lxnfua_clipPathFallback"><div class="sticky z-2 select-none top-(--sticky-padding-top)"><div class="flex w-full items-center justify-between py-1.5 ps-4 pe-1.5 font-sans md:ps-5 bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary"><div class="flex max-w-[75%] min-w-0 cursor-default items-center text-sm font-medium justify-self-start text-token-text-primary"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-sm me-2.5 shrink-0"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-ni7q5mnh.svg#e45ab3" fill="currentColor"></use></svg>Python</div><div class="flex flex-row items-center gap-0.5 justify-self-end"><button class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none py-2 text-sm font-medium hover:bg-black/5 dark:hover:bg-white/10 size-9 rounded-full px-2" aria-label="Copy" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-md"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-ni7q5mnh.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button><button class="btn relative group-focus-within/dialog:focus-visible:[outline-width:1.5px] group-focus-within/dialog:focus-visible:[outline-offset:2.5px] group-focus-within/dialog:focus-visible:[outline-style:solid] group-focus-within/dialog:focus-visible:[outline-color:var(--text-primary)] btn-ghost border-token-border-default ms-2 border font-sans" aria-label="Run code" type="button"><div class="flex w-full items-center justify-center gap-1.5"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-label="" class="-ms-0.5 icon"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-ni7q5mnh.svg#6ef7a4" fill="currentColor"></use></svg>Run</div></button></div></div></div><div class="pointer-events-none absolute inset-x-4 top-12 bottom-4"><div class="pointer-events-none sticky z-40 shrink-0 z-1!" style="top: calc(calc(var(--sticky-padding-top) + 48px) - 1px * 3); margin-bottom: calc(-4px); height: calc(4px); mask-image: linear-gradient(transparent 25%, white 75%);"><div class="sticky bg-token-border-light" style="top: calc(var(--sticky-padding-top) + 48px); height: 1px;"></div></div></div><div class="" style="transform: none;"><div class="relative z-0 flex max-w-full"><div id="code-block-viewer" dir="ltr" class="q9tKkq_viewer cm-editor z-10 light:cm-light dark:cm-light flex h-full w-full flex-col items-stretch ͼk ͼy"><div class="cm-scroller"><div class="cm-content q9tKkq_readonly"><span class="ͼn">def</span><span> </span><span class="ͼt">_load_selected_account</span><span>(</span><span class="ͼt">self</span><span>):</span><br><br><span>    </span><span class="ͼt">item</span><span> </span><span class="ͼn">=</span><span> </span><span class="ͼt">self</span><span class="ͼn">.</span><span>account_list</span><span class="ͼn">.</span><span>currentItem()</span><br><br><span>    </span><span class="ͼn">if</span><span> </span><span class="ͼn">not</span><span> </span><span class="ͼt">item</span><span>:</span><br><span>        </span><span class="ͼn">return</span><br><br><span>    </span><span class="ͼt">name</span><span> </span><span class="ͼn">=</span><span> </span><span class="ͼt">item</span><span class="ͼn">.</span><span>text()</span><br><br><span>    </span><span class="ͼt">creds</span><span> </span><span class="ͼn">=</span><span> </span><span class="ͼt">CredentialManager</span><span class="ͼn">.</span><span>load_account(</span><span class="ͼt">name</span><span>)</span><br><br><span>    </span><span class="ͼn">if</span><span> </span><span class="ͼn">not</span><span> </span><span class="ͼt">creds</span><span>:</span><br><span>        </span><span class="ͼn">return</span><br><br><span>    </span><span class="ͼt">broker</span><span> </span><span class="ͼn">=</span><span> </span><span class="ͼt">creds</span><span>[</span><span class="ͼr">"broker"</span><span>]</span><br><br><span>    </span><span class="ͼt">self</span><span class="ͼn">.</span><span>exchange_type_box</span><span class="ͼn">.</span><span>setCurrentText(</span><span class="ͼt">broker</span><span>[</span><span class="ͼr">"type"</span><span>])</span><br><br><span>    </span><span class="ͼt">self</span><span class="ͼn">.</span><span>_update_exchange_list(</span><span class="ͼt">broker</span><span>[</span><span class="ͼr">"type"</span><span>])</span><br><br><span>    </span><span class="ͼt">self</span><span class="ͼn">.</span><span>exchange_box</span><span class="ͼn">.</span><span>setCurrentText(</span><span class="ͼt">broker</span><span>[</span><span class="ͼr">"exchange"</span><span>])</span><br><br><span>    </span><span class="ͼt">self</span><span class="ͼn">.</span><span>api_input</span><span class="ͼn">.</span><span>setText(</span><span class="ͼt">broker</span><span class="ͼn">.</span><span>get(</span><span class="ͼr">"api_key"</span><span>, </span><span class="ͼr">""</span><span>))</span><br><span>    </span><span class="ͼt">self</span><span class="ͼn">.</span><span>secret_input</span><span class="ͼn">.</span><span>setText(</span><span class="ͼt">broker</span><span class="ͼn">.</span><span>get(</span><span class="ͼr">"secret"</span><span>, </span><span class="ͼr">""</span><span>))</span><br><br><span>    </span><span class="ͼt">self</span><span class="ͼn">.</span><span>mode_box</span><span class="ͼn">.</span><span>setCurrentText(</span><span class="ͼt">broker</span><span class="ͼn">.</span><span>get(</span><span class="ͼr">"mode"</span><span>, </span><span class="ͼr">"paper"</span><span>))</span><br><br><span>    </span><span class="ͼt">self</span><span class="ͼn">.</span><span>risk_input</span><span class="ͼn">.</span><span>setValue(</span><br><span>        </span><span class="ͼt">creds</span><span class="ͼn">.</span><span>get(</span><span class="ͼr">"risk"</span><span>, {})</span><span class="ͼn">.</span><span>get(</span><span class="ͼr">"risk_percent"</span><span>, </span><span class="ͼq">2</span><span>)</span><br><span>    )</span><br><br><span>    </span><span class="ͼt">self</span><span class="ͼn">.</span><span>strategy_box</span><span class="ͼn">.</span><span>setCurrentText(</span><br><span>        </span><span class="ͼt">creds</span><span class="ͼn">.</span><span>get(</span><span class="ͼr">"strategy"</span><span>, </span><span class="ͼr">"EMA_CROSS"</span><span>)</span><br><span>    )</span></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=""><div class="" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"></div></div></div></div></div></pre>
