<p data-start="1511" data-end="1533">Now the broker exists.</p>
<hr data-start="1535" data-end="1538">
<h1 data-section-id="qxouij" data-start="1540" data-end="1558">⚠️ Another Issue</h1>
<p data-start="1560" data-end="1609">Your <code data-start="1565" data-end="1582">fetch_symbols()</code> probably is <strong data-start="1595" data-end="1608">not async</strong>.</p>
<p data-start="1611" data-end="1675">Most CCXT calls are async, but <code data-start="1642" data-end="1658">load_markets()</code> returns markets.</p>
<p data-start="1677" data-end="1719">Better implementation inside <code data-start="1706" data-end="1718">CCXTBroker</code>.</p>
<hr data-start="1721" data-end="1724">
